  {name:'Ijji 4',website:'ijjisushiandhibachi.com',address:'10580 N Mccarran Blvd Ste 102',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89523',phone:'(775) 507-4554',categories: ['Korean',' Barbeque',' Chicken Wings'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"Closed","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Great Basin Brewing Co. - Reno',website:'greatbasinbrewingco.com',address:'5525 S Virginia St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89502',phone:'(775) 284-7711',categories: ['American (New)',' Brewpubs'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM"\}',about:'We brew craft beer that speaks to the wild at heart, modern-day pioneers and those who refuse to settle. Our beer elevates the experiences of everyone as well as fuels the greater good by helping to make the world a better place, one brew at a time.',history:'Established in 1993. Great Basin Brewing Company started out as a small hometown craft brewery with one location in Sparks, Nevada in 1993. We were honored to win 2 major medals at the Great American Beer Festival the year after opening. Years later in 2010 we opened our second location in Reno, Nevada in order to meet local demand for our craft beer and food. To this day we continue to be Nevada\'s most award-winning brewery.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Arario Midtown',website:'arariomidtown.com',address:'777 S Center St Ste 200',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89501',phone:'(775) 870-8202',categories: ['Korean',' Gluten-Free',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"Closed","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"3:00 PM - 9:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Ijji 2 Sushi & Japanese Steakhouse',website:'ijjisushiandhibachi.com',address:'4955 S Virginia St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89502',phone:'(775) 825-6688',categories: ['Sushi Bars',' Steakhouses',' Japanese'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Welcome to the home of Ijji Sushi and Hibachi steakhouse. We are the premier Sushi and Hibachi restaurant of Reno and Sparks with a CAB certification for top quality meat. We pride ourselves on excellent customer satisfaction and the highest grade of our food for sushi and hibachi. Our Fish and Seafood is delivered fresh daily from well known local distributors, our unique salad bar makes Ijji Sushi to be one of a kind in Reno, Nevada. Ijji sushi offers the most spacious sushi restaurant in the area with the capacity to accommodate up to two hundred guests. Our customers are our top priority therefore our staff will go the extra mile to make your dining experience a one of a kind. Ijji Sushi brings to you The Authentic Japanese food without leaving Reno Nevada; our skilled chefs will entertain you with a live show while cooking in front of you as part of the Hibachi tradition.',history:'Established in 2011. We are part of Mintan Corporation established in northern Nevada on 2005. Our first sushi restaurant opened its doors in the beautiful city of Sparks on September of 2008. Thanks to the loyalty of our customers and community we proudly opened our second restaurant in December of 2011 in "The Biggest Little City of the World" Reno, NV. Our restaurants were established with a vision in mind to provide you with a comfortable, spacious and modern dining atmosphere. Come and satisfy your taste buds and try one of our tantalizing long rolls. We offer hibachi, all you can eat sushi, over ten different domestic or import beers on tap and SAKE.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Hinoki Sushi',website:'facebook.com/HinokiSushi',address:'5270 Longley Ln',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89511',phone:'(775) 409-4994',categories: ['Sushi Bars',' Japanese',' Seafood'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Old Granite Street Eatery',website:'oldgranitestreeteatery.com',address:'243 S Sierra St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89501',phone:'(775) 622-3222',categories: ['American (New)',' American (Traditional)'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Fri":"10:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 8:00 PM"\}',about:'Located at 243 S. Sierra St. in a building erected in 1940, specifically for a restaurant, is the home of a unique new gathering place. The original address was 243 Granite St. hence the name...Old Granite Street Eatery. With a menu that reflects a strong desire to provide familiar, comforting dishes having an emphasis on quality ingredients. Combined with constantly rotating craft beer selections, focused wine options and hand crafted cocktails, Old Granite Street Eatery looks to be a casual affordable everyday option for neighbors and community to share in great food and drink. Highlighted by a Saturday and Sunday brunch, Granite Street is open daily on the remaining days at 11am with the kitchen remaining open until midnight. A handful of small party reservations will be taken daily, with a large community table and bar available strictly for walk-in dining and/or imbibing.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'BJ\'s Nevada Barbecue',website:'bjsbbq.com',address:'80 E Victorian Ave',city:'Sparks',state:'NV',zipcode:'89431',phone:'(775) 355-1010',categories: ['Barbeque',' Breakfast & Brunch',' American (Traditional)'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Closed","Tue":"6:30 AM - 8:30 PM","Wed":"6:30 AM - 8:30 PM","Thu":"6:30 AM - 8:30 PM","Fri":"6:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"7:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"Closed"\}',about:'Family owned and operated since 1986, BJ\'s serves authentic Southern barbecue and classic American homemade breakfast in a casual, family-friendly atmosphere. Event catering also available. We put our heart and soul into our recipes and hope you enjoy your visit. Please don’t hesitate to speak with your server if there’s an issue with something. Thank you for supporting this local business.',history:'Established in 1986. BJ\'s Nevada Barbecue Company has been family-owned by the Rathmanns since 1986. Peter and Roberta Rathmann, and their kids Jay and Kelly, continue to oversee every part of the restaurant\'s operation and success.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Texas Roadhouse',website:'texasroadhouse.com',address:'150 Damonte Ranch Pkwy',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89521',phone:'(775) 852-6333',categories: ['American (Traditional)',' Steakhouses',' Barbeque'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"3:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"3:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"3:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"3:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'At Texas Roadhouse in Reno, NV we like to brag about our Hand-Cut Steaks, Fall-Off-The-Bone Ribs, Made-From-Scratch Sides, and Fresh-Baked Bread. Everything we do goes into making our hearty meals stand out. We handcraft almost everything we serve. We provide larger portions so you get more food for your dollar. And if you want an Ice Cold Beer or Legendary Margarita to wash it all down\' well, we have those, too. Our food\'s not the only thing that\'s Legendary at the Roadhouse\' our fun is too. From our line dancers to our jukebox to our friendly servers, you\'ll enjoy every second you spend in a Texas Roadhouse. The Texas Roadhouse story is simple. Legendary Food, Legendary Service\' all with lots of Legendary Fun.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Grimaldi\'s Pizzeria',website:'grimaldispizzeria.com',address:'1180 Scheels Dr Ste B-117',city:'Sparks',state:'NV',zipcode:'89434',phone:'(775) 260-4634',categories: ['Pizza',' Desserts',' Beer',' Wine & Spirits'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Grimaldi\'s Pizzeria is a Brooklyn-style coal brick oven pizzeria. Our fresh ingredients, handmade mozzarella, fresh dough and pizza sauce make us the most award-winning pizzeria in the United States.',history:'Established in 2003. Grimaldi\'s Pizzeria serves traditional coal fired brick-oven pizza using pizza-making traditions which includes only fresh ingredients, a "secret recipe" pizza sauce, handmade mozzarella cheese and dough, originating in Brooklyn over 100 years ago.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Beefy\'s',website:'beefysreno.com',address:'1300 S Virginia St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89502',phone:'(775) 870-1333',categories: ['Diners',' Burgers',' Sandwiches'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Sun":"Closed"\}',about:'Some of the best burgers and hot dogs in Reno. We now offer great chicken wings. Grilled cheese sandwiches and BLT\'s. Shoestring French Fries and Onion Rings. Chili Con Carne and Daily Specials. Soft Serve Ice Cream and Milkshakes. Large selection of Craft beer and wine available. Super friendly service and great food! One of the oldest dining establishments in Reno, the building is an original Valentines Diner. The location has been listed in the National Register of Historic Places! Effective December 13,2021, Beefy\'s has re-opened inside dining (limited to the original 8 seats!)',history:'Established in 1947. An original Valentine diner, this establishment got its start in 1947 as Landrum\'s. Over the course of the years, while Reno has grown, Beefy\'s still remains in the original location. A small cozy diner-like atmosphere, great service and food make this a Reno must.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Brothers Barbecue',website:'bbqreno.com',address:'618 S Center St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89501',phone:'(775) 384-3547',categories: ['Barbeque'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Closed","Tue":"11:00 AM - 7:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 7:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 7:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 7:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 6:00 PM","Sun":"Closed"\}',about:'Brothers Barbecue specializes in some of the Best Texas Barbecue in Nevada. We smoke fresh daily with generations of family recipes and real wood smoked meats. We offer daily specials to highlight our low and slow smoked meats including beef ribs, brisket, St. Louis cut pork ribs and turkey breast to name a few. We also use our own rubs and make our own barbecue sauce.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Ruby River Steakhouse',website:'rubyriver.com',address:'2750 S Virginia St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89502',phone:'(775) 827-4007',categories: ['Steakhouses',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Seafood'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"4:00 PM - 8:30 PM","Tue":"4:00 PM - 8:30 PM","Wed":"4:00 PM - 8:30 PM","Thu":"4:00 PM - 8:30 PM","Fri":"4:00 PM - 9:30 PM","Sat":"4:00 PM - 9:30 PM","Sun":"4:00 PM - 8:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Brasserie Saint James',website:'brasseriesaintjames.com',address:'901 S Center St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89501',phone:'(775) 348-8888',categories: ['Brasseries',' Breweries'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Closed","Tue":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 8:00 PM"\}',about:'Award winning craft beers, unique pub fare, and elevated comfort food.',history:'Established in 2012. Opened in October 2012, in the historic "Crystal Water and Ice" building. The building\'s original construction was in 1929. The artesian lake located 285 feet below the building supplies all the water to our brewery and restaurant. Winner of the Great American Beer Festival "Best Midsized Brewpub" in 2014.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Lili\'s Restaurant & Bar',website:'lilisdining.com',address:'2325 Kietzke Ln',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89502',phone:'(775) 826-7777',categories: ['American (Traditional)',' Venues & Event Spaces'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Tue":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Wed":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Thu":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Fri":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Sat":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Sun":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM"\}',about:'The best breakfast lunch and dinner in Reno!',history:'Established in 2009. always the freshest ingredients, fast friendly service and the lowest prices in town!',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Crawfish Asian Cuisine',website:'crawfishasiancuisine.com',address:'1296 E Plumb Ln Ste H',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89502',phone:'(775) 710-3168',categories: ['Chinese',' Asian Fusion',' Cajun/Creole'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Closed","Tue":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 8:30 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 8:30 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Coffeebar',website:'coffeebar.com',address:'682 Mt Rose St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89509',phone:'(775) 800-1090',categories: ['Coffee & Tea',' Cafes',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$',hours:'\{"Mon":"6:00 AM - 6:00 PM","Tue":"6:00 AM - 6:00 PM","Wed":"6:00 AM - 6:00 PM","Thu":"6:00 AM - 6:00 PM","Fri":"6:00 AM - 6:00 PM","Sat":"6:00 AM - 6:00 PM","Sun":"6:00 AM - 6:00 PM"\}',about:'Coffeebar is the fuel that propels you throughout your day. Inspired by the Italian coffee bar culture, we believe we are Hospitalians first, baristas and chefs second. Making people feel good is our M.O. Founded in Truckee, CA in 2010, Coffeebar was built off of over two decades of coffee industry knowledge. But at the end of the day, we\'re only as good as the next cup we make. Our locations provide the best coffee, breakfast, pastries, and snacks in the area.',user: User.find(2)},
