  {name:'Great Basin Brewing Co. - Sparks',website:'greatbasinbrewingco.com',address:'846 Victorian Ave',city:'Sparks',state:'NV',zipcode:'89431',phone:'(775) 355-7711',categories: ['American (New)',' Brewpubs'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM"\}',about:'We brew craft beer that speaks to the wild at heart, modern-day pioneers and those who refuse to settle. Our beer elevates the experiences of everyone as well as fuels the greater good by helping to make the world a better place, one brew at a time.',history:'Established in 1993. Tom was a geologist with a love of homebrewing. He had a chance to follow that dream, so in 1993 he took a chance and opened Great Basin Brewing Company. It turned out to be a success and continues to grow in business and beer fans.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Sierra St Kitchen & Cocktails',website:'sierrastkitchen.com',address:'50 North Sierra St Ste 103',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89501',phone:'(775) 686-6669',categories: ['Cocktail Bars',' Tapas/Small Plates',' American (New)'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"4:30 PM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"4:30 PM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"4:30 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"4:30 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"4:30 PM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"12:00 PM - 9:30 PM","Sun":"3:00 PM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Voted best NEW Restaurants FOR 2016. Voted best Tapas-small plates 2019 Voted best local space 2022 We have a great location downtown Reno by the river and movies. We feature a fresh small plates menu with lots of variety (lamb, filet, lobster, Hawaiian ahi tuna,shell fish, vegetarian, gluten free, crab cakes). NEW ENTREE additions. Craft made cocktails. A great wine list and craft beers from around the world. Our servers are friendly and knowledgeable Late night dining. Great wine list. Cocktails hand crafted. Happy hour features. Exceptional and friendly service. Great food. Heart of Downtown. All of this makes up the total experience at Sierra St. Easy PARKING -garage right at first and Sierra st.',history:'Established in 2016. RATED as One of the BEST NEW Restaurants FOR 2016. We at Sierra St Kitchen & Cocktails are serious about our food, service and hand crafted liquor offerings. Our Kitchen includes our talented kitchen crew. We strives to produce the best for our guests on a daily basis and are quality driven.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Churrasco Brazilian Steakhouse',website:'churrascobr.com',address:'425 S Virginia St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89501',phone:'(775) 322-4000',categories: ['Brazilian',' Steakhouses',' Buffets'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:00 PM - 8:00 PM","Tue":"5:00 PM - 8:00 PM","Wed":"5:00 PM - 8:00 PM","Thu":"5:00 PM - 8:00 PM","Fri":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"12:00 PM - 2:30 PM,4:30 PM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"12:00 PM - 2:30 PM,4:30 PM - 8:00 PM"\}',about:'Churrasco Brazilian Steakhouse specializes in treating guests to an unforgettable Brazilian steakhouse experience through our chef-driven cuisine, world-class full bar, and unparalleled hospitality. We offer 15 all you can eat rotisserie grilled meats which are sliced directly from the skewer to your plate. We also offer a full variety of hot sides and chilled salads at our fresh market table including imported cheeses and traditional dishes (please see our fresh market table menu at Churrascobr.com). Our traditional rodizio dining experience includes both the buffet and all you can eat meat for one set price, with discounts for children or "buffet only" selections. Churrasco is the winner of the Best of Reno (The Reno Gazette Journal\'s official community choice awards) as Reno\'s Best New Restaurant in 2022, also a finalist as Best Steakhouse in Reno in 2023! We are open 7 nights a week for dinner and for lunch on the weekends. We provide masks, gloves and hand sanitizer at the buffet if you choose to use them. Gift cards available online. Find menu, delivery menu, parking, pricing and more at Churrascobr.com',history:'Established in 2020. Churrasco Brazilian Steakhouse opened in midtown Reno, NV in February, 2020 and is not a part of any chain. Locals voted Churrasco Brazilian Steakhouse the "Best New Restaurant" in Reno in 2021 & 2022; and top 3 Best Steakhouse in Reno Nevada.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'The Cheesecake Factory',website:'thecheesecakefactory.com',address:'5162 Meadowood Mall Cir',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89502',phone:'(775) 826-4107',categories: ['American (Traditional)',' Desserts',' Seafood'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'The Cheesecake Factory offers something for everyone featuring a wide variety of over 200 menu items prepared fresh to order each day, plus over 30 legendary varieties of the Finest Cheesecake.',user: User.find(2)},
