  {name:'Moo Dang',website:'thaimoodang.com',address:'1565 S Virginia St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89502',phone:'(775) 420-4267',categories: ['Thai',' Soup',' Noodles'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Closed","Tue":"11:30 AM - 8:30 PM","Wed":"11:30 AM - 8:30 PM","Thu":"11:30 AM - 8:30 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 8:30 PM","Sat":"11:30 AM - 8:30 PM","Sun":"3:00 PM - 8:30 PM"\}',about:'Red Roast Pork, Thai Noodle Soups, desserts, Craft Beer, Wine, and More! We have plenty of vegetarian, vegan and gluten-free options, as well as chicken, beef, and shrimp. Togo orders packed in eco-friendly containers to keep you fed and the earth green. If you are in the mood for Phad Thai, papaya salad, Tom yum soup, panang curry, drunken noodles, mango and sticky rice, or just a nice cold Singha beer, we have you covered! Tell us how spicy you would like it and we can make it extra mild or extra spicy hot! Come see us in midtown Reno!',history:'Established in 2015. Moo Dang Opened May 15, 2015 All the way from Bangkok, and across Thailand, Moo Dang has landed in Reno, Nevada! Located in midtown Reno with parking and close to the airport convention center downtown and Costco',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'The Cup Café',website:'breakfastatkimmies.com',address:'6770 S Virginia St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89511',phone:'(775) 853-4952',categories: ['Breakfast & Brunch',' American (Traditional)',' Sandwiches'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"6:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Tue":"6:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Wed":"6:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Thu":"6:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Fri":"6:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Sat":"6:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Sun":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Kwok\'s Bistro',website:'kwoksbistro.com',address:'275 West St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89501',phone:'(775) 507-7270',categories: ['Chinese',' Asian Fusion'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Closed","Tue":"4:00 PM - 8:00 PM","Wed":"4:00 PM - 8:00 PM","Thu":"4:00 PM - 8:00 PM","Fri":"4:00 PM - 8:00 PM","Sat":"4:00 PM - 8:00 PM","Sun":"4:00 PM - 8:00 PM"\}',about:'From traditional clay pots to pork belly sliders to late night congee, Kwok brings the best asian fusion to downtown Reno.',history:'Established in 2018. We started renovations and construction in February of 2018.The restaurant has new and custom equipment fabricated out of San Francisco. We officially opened for business on March 30, 2018.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Laughing Planet',website:'laughingplanet.com',address:'650 Tahoe S',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89509',phone:'(775) 360-2592',categories: ['Vegetarian',' Salad',' Gluten-Free'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'We are a quick-service cafe that serves nutritious fare in the form of tasty burritos, bowls, soups, salads, smoothies, juices and home-made cookies. We use mostly locally sourced and organic ingredients all appropriately farmed and raised.',history:'Established in 2014. Actually started in Bloomington Indiana in 1995. There are 16 stores world wide and we started in Reno in 2014',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Lucky Beaver Bar & Burger',website:'luckybeaver.com',address:'3655 S Virginia St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89502',phone:'(775) 829-8500',categories: ['American (Traditional)',' Sports Bars',' Burgers'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Open 24 hours","Tue":"Open 24 hours","Wed":"Open 24 hours","Thu":"Open 24 hours","Fri":"Open 24 hours","Sat":"Open 24 hours","Sun":"Open 24 hours"\}',about:'Our story is a short one but a good one. Two local businessmen wanted to open a restaurant that would serve quality food, great cocktails and a fun gaming environment. They looked at the Old Bills Casino on Highway 50 in Stateline NV, and wanted to bring some life back to the classic building. Our restaurant was opened on July 4, 2012 and has been a very popular spot for both locals and tourists. Since the day we opened our guests have been championing our Burgers as the best in the state of Nevada and some say the best in the country. That is a bold claim but check out our recommendations on Facebook or our reviews on Yelp to confirm it. Pat LaFrieda, famous from his family\'s meat purveyor business and the Food Network created our patty. It is a combination of chuck roast and short rib that is meshed together and then chopped into a 1/2 pound patty. The patty is cooked to perfection on our custom grill and this is what makes it so outstanding. Our logo was not created specifically for us, it is a famous painting in the Southern California community. The painting was done in 1981 and the model, whose name is Clementine, was the artists\' girlfriend at the time. She is laying on a classic Chris Craft boat in Newport Harbor. The artist, Gary Miltimore of Newport Ca, gave us permission to use it as he is a personal friend of our owners. We have now opened our second location in Reno and look forward to many additional locations.',history:'Established in 2014. Our story is a short one but a good one. Two local businessmen wanted to open a restaurant that would serve quality food, great cocktails and a fun gaming environment. They looked at the Old Bills Casino on Highway 50 in Stateline NV, and wanted to bring some life back to the classic building. Our first restaurant was opened on July 4, 2012 and has been a very popular spot for both locals and tourists. Since the day we opened our guests have been championing our Burgers and Steaks as the best in the state of Nevada and some say the best in the country. That is a bold claim but check out our recommendations on Facebook or our reviews on Yelp to confirm it. Pat LaFrieda, famous from his family\'s meat purveyor business and the Food Network created our patty. It is a combination of chuck roast and short rib that is meshed together and then chopped into a 1/2 pound patty. The patty is cooked to perfection on our custom rotating grill and this is what makes it so outstanding.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Sushi Rose',website:'renosushirose.com',address:'2005 Sierra Highlands Dr Ste 147A',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89523',phone:'(775) 747-1888',categories: ['Sushi Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Pho 777 Vietnamese Noodle Restaurant',website:'pho.com',address:'102 E 2nd St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89501',phone:'(775) 323-7777',categories: ['Vietnamese',' Noodles'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"10:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"10:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"10:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"10:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"10:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Vietnamese Noodle Restaurant. Pho Restaurant',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'ijji Noodle House & Poke Don',website:'ijjireno.com',address:'199 Damonte Ranch Pkwy Ste 8M',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89521',phone:'(775) 870-1198',categories: ['Noodles',' Vietnamese',' Ramen'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Hot, flavorful ramen, pho, and asian cuisine dishes that will have your mouth watering!',history:'Established in 2019. Ijji Noodle House brings the comfort food from Asia to Reno! We serve a variety of different Asian style dishes, so everyone is happy! Enjoy a warm bowl of Vietnamese Pho or Japanese Ramen, along with a variety of traditional appetizers, and other styles including Chinese, or BBQ dishes. Come visit us today for an all around authentic, fast-paced experience you will never forget! Ijjji Poke Don, Enjoy a customizable fresh poke bowl with your choice of 7different types of protein, many different sauces, and a multitude of your favorite toppings. We strive to serve you the best poke bowl in town!',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Roxy',website:'eldoradoreno.com',address:'345 N Virginia St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89501',phone:'(775) 785-9066',categories: ['Bars',' Steakhouses',' Seafood'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Roxy\'s chefs hand-select top cuts of meats, poultry and fish to create exquisite entrées prepared in a specialty wood-fired oven. Roxy\'s wait staff has a vast knowledge of fine wines and liquors and expert pastry chefs create scrumptious breads, soufflés, tarts, sorbets and more, in an exhibition bakery.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Tha Joint Sushi & Grill',website:'thajointsushi.com',address:'222 Los Altos Pkwy Ste 112 - 114',city:'Sparks',state:'NV',zipcode:'89436',phone:'(775) 626-8677',categories: ['Sushi Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Specialized in All you can eat Sushi and limited grilled items for Korean Fusion Dish.',history:'Established in 2010. Sushi chefs with great experiences have come together to open a new business in town of a great sushi Trend. Opened in March, 2010 in fast growing city in northern nevada.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Charlie Palmer Steak Reno',website:'charliepalmer.com',address:'2500 2nd St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89595',phone:'(775) 789-2456',categories: ['Steakhouses',' Wine Bars',' American (New)'],price:'$$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Chihuahua\'s Cantina & Grill',website:'chihuahuasgrill.com',address:'7111 S Virginia St Ste C',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89511',phone:'(775) 683-9846',categories: ['Mexican',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"10:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'It all began with our family\'s love for traditional Mexican food. A love that not only became our passion, but the reason we decided to open Chihuahua\'s Cantina & Grill here in Nevada. With each bite, we strive to honor generations past. That\'s why you\'ll find our recipes blend secret ingredients with strict attention to freshness and quality -- the foundation to our wholesome, authentic cuisine. But that\'s certainly not all we have to offer when you dine with us. From our sports-friendly atmosphere to our welcoming service, we\'re the perfect place to enjoy a delicious meal with friends and family. We even offer 14 draft beers and an incredible selection of tequila, mezcal, and cocktails. So the next time you\'re in the neighborhood, we welcome you to stop by for a taste of flavors rich in history.',history:'Established in 2004. Began in Winnemucca, NV and became a popular destination for people driving through the area and locals. In 2018, we opened our second location in Reno, NV. Since inception, our goal has been to provide unmatched, fresh Mexican food and drinks in a more modern and inviting location than the traditional Mexican Restaurant, but with great value prices.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Ijji Sushi',website:'ijjireno.com',address:'685 E Prater Way Ste 101',city:'Sparks',state:'NV',zipcode:'89431',phone:'(775) 356-8668',categories: ['Sushi Bars',' Desserts'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'When guests arrive at Ijji, they\'re greeted by a warm, attentive staff. And when they sit down, they can choose from a menu full of fresh ingredients and a ton of variety (about 100 sushi rolls). Our inviting space is known for hosting large celebrations and for the vivacious chefs that occupy the hibachi grills. We want to offer the best to our community, which means you\'ll see families spending quality time together and friends unwinding at our bar. But we\'re more than a gathering place for sushi and teppanyaki lovers -- we\'re also a local tradition nearly a decade in the making.',history:'Established in 2011. We are part of Mintan Corporation, established in northern Nevada in 2005. Our first sushi restaurant opened its doors in the beautiful city of Sparks in September of 2008. Thanks to the loyalty of our customers and community, we proudly opened our second restaurant in December of 2011 in "The Biggest Little City in the World," Reno, NV. Our restaurants were established with a vision in mind to provide you with a comfortable, spacious, and modern dining atmosphere.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Archie\'s Giant Hamburgers & Breakfast',website:'archiesreno.com',address:'2195 N Virginia St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89503',phone:'(775) 322-9595',categories: ['Burgers',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Sports Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"6:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"6:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"6:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"6:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Fri":"6:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"6:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"6:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'We serve up some of Reno\'s favorite dishes. We are known for our delicious burgers and the best breakfast in Reno. The quaint diner on the lower level is warm and welcoming, the perfect setting to enjoy Archie\'s French Toast or Chicken Fried Steak and Eggs. The upper deck features high definition flat screens, a jukebox, video poker at the bar and the best view of the city. Throughout the years, Archie\'s has always been loyal to its customers. Whether it\'s game time, a night out with friends, or a family meal, the comforting food and friendly service keeps people coming back.',history:'Established in 1995. Archie\'s Giant Hamburgers & Breakfast has been serving up delicious plates for 24 years now and has come a long way since their beginnings in 1995. The Alumni owned and operated restaurant is located on Virginia Street, directly across from the University of Nevada, Reno. It was expanded in the spring of 2007 and now duals as a two-story diner and sports bar. You\'ll also find Wolf Pack sports memorabilia hanging on the walls. Archie\'s is a huge supporter of the Nevada Wolf Pack, they even named a burger after it! The World Famous Wolf Pack (a double meat and double cheese burger) is one of the many famous burgers served at Archie\'s.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Squeeze In',website:'squeezein.com',address:'5020 Las Brisas Blvd Ste A5',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89523',phone:'(775) 787-2700',categories: ['Breakfast & Brunch',' American (Traditional)'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"7:30 AM - 2:00 PM","Tue":"7:30 AM - 2:00 PM","Wed":"7:30 AM - 2:00 PM","Thu":"7:30 AM - 2:00 PM","Fri":"7:30 AM - 2:00 PM","Sat":"7:30 AM - 2:00 PM","Sun":"7:30 AM - 2:00 PM"\}',about:'Welcome to Squeeze In - Your Ultimate Breakfast & Brunch Destination! 50 Years ago a tiny kitchen in the little ski town of Truckee California was serving up omelettes and mimosas to locals and tourists alike. Now with multiple corporate and franchise locations throughout the west coast, The Squeeze In is growing a legacy of upbeat environments, delicious food, work/life balance, meaningful community intergration, and is a high-demand, low cost profitable business model for those seeking franchising opportunities. The Squeeze In is most famous for: "The Best Omelettes on the Planet!" something celebrity chef Bobby Flay filmed a show about, and the menu features the Food Network omelettes Racy Tracy and Spanish Flay in tribure of the recognition. However, it\'s the undeniable feel-good vibe that keep guests coming back time and time again. What makes a feel good vibe? Happy people, in a fun environment, serving wholesome food, and making positive impact on communities. Plus mimosas, bloody marys, bright walls that you can sign with a sharpie, an alien mascot, toy baskets for kids and good tunes all help with the feel good vibe too. We\'re open from 7:30-2:00pm every day except Thanksgiving and Christmas, and we hope to have the pleasure to serve you breakfast, brunch, or lunch at one of our locations soon!',history:'Established in 1974. Opened in Historic Downtown Truckee, California in May 1974 at 10060 Donner Pass Road. Second location opened in Northwest Reno, Nevada at 5020 Las Brisas Boulevard (at McCarran and Las Brisas) in February, 2008. Third location opened on April 1, 2011 in South Reno at 25 Foothill Road (at South Meadows Parkway and South Virginia Street, Nevada. The Downtown Truckee Squeeze In got its name from its tiny-ness: 10\'3\'\' wide and 62 feet deep. 14 tables, that\'s it in Truckee. Northwest Squeeze seats 114 inside, and when the weather\'s nice, we can seat an additional 46 guests on our patio. Well-behaved and leashed pets are welcome on the patio. We\'ll even hook \'em up with a bowl of water and some dog food from King\'s Row Pet Hospital. The South Reno location is the largest of the three, with a seating capacity of up to 150 guests, and even more on the patio when open. All three locations are open 7am to 2pm everyday, 363 days a year. Weekends are busiest, so come early or late, or wait!',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Bimini Steakhouse',website:'peppermillreno.com/dining/fine-dining/bimini-steakhouse/',address:'2707 S Virginia St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89502',phone:'(775) 826-2121',categories: ['Steakhouses'],price:'$$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:30 PM - 9:30 PM","Tue":"5:30 PM - 9:30 PM","Wed":"5:30 PM - 9:30 PM","Thu":"5:30 PM - 9:30 PM","Fri":"5:30 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"5:30 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"5:30 PM - 9:30 PM"\}',about:'Savor hardwood grilled steaks, chops and seafood in an unparalleled atmosphere.',user: User.find(2)},
