  {name:'Brew Brothers',website:'caesars.com/eldorado-reno/restaurants/brew-brothers',address:'345 N Virginia St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89501',phone:'(775) 785-9047',categories: ['Breweries',' Burgers',' Pizza'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Named Best Brewpub in America by Nightclub & Bar magazine, The Brew Brothers offers eight custom microbrews and a creative menu, including gourmet wood-fired pizzas, salads, burgers, ribs, sandwiches, homemade soups and complete dinners.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Bawarchi Indian Cuisine',website:'bawarchibiryanis.com',address:'9333 Double R Blvd Ste 600',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89521',phone:'(775) 800-6363',categories: ['Indian'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Closed","Tue":"11:30 AM - 2:30 PM,5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:30 AM - 2:30 PM,5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:30 AM - 2:30 PM,5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 3:00 PM,5:00 PM - 9:30 PM","Sat":"11:30 AM - 9:30 PM","Sun":"11:30 AM - 9:30 PM"\}',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Butcher\'s Kitchen CHAR-B-QUE',website:'bkcharbque.com',address:'7689 S Virginia St Ste N',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89511',phone:'(775) 499-5855',categories: ['Barbeque',' Sandwiches',' Burgers'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Sun":"Closed"\}',about:'We specialize in Butcher inspired sandwiches, Burritos an entrees using a wood fired grill, smoker, as well as a rotisserie.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Liberty Food & Wine Exchange',website:'libertyfoodandwine.com',address:'100 N Sierra St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89501',phone:'(775) 336-1091',categories: ['Bars',' American (New)',' Pizza'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'We have set up an online store and shopping area in our restaurant where you can pick up orders curbside or come in and grab a few essentials. Come by for great prices on all your Liberty Favorites.',history:'Established in 2017. We are an artisan eatery, market and bar. We offer small, handcrafted plates, house-cured meat, artisan breads and pastas, an international wine selection and handcrafted cocktails and beer.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Atlantis Bistro Napa',website:'atlantiscasino.com/dining/fine-dining/atlantis-bistro-napa',address:'3800 S Virginia St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89502',phone:'(775) 335-4539',categories: ['American (New)',' Seafood',' Wine Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Savor contemporary cuisine inspired by Napa Valley with emphasis on seasonal, organic ingredients and simple, fresh flavors. Bistro Napa offers innovative dishes, a Raw Seafood Bar featuring the finest oysters from the Pacific Northwest, and cutting-edge cocktails infused with fresh fruit purees, boutique liquors and bitters. The sommelier will help complement any Bistro experience with thoughtfully chosen wine from our 4,000-bottle wine cellar.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'SouthCreek Pizza',website:'southcreekpizza.com',address:'45 Foothill Rd',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89511',phone:'(775) 622-1620',categories: ['Pizza'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Closed","Tue":"3:00 PM - 8:00 PM","Wed":"3:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"3:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"12:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"1:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"4:00 PM - 8:00 PM"\}',about:'Hand Crafted--Wood Fired--Brick Oven Pizza is what SouthCreek Pizza is all about. We use the freshest ingredients available, locally sourced if possible. In addition, we have salads, small plates including Meatballs, and Fire Roasted Veggies, Salumi and Cheese Plates. Our Pizza selections include Naples style pies, SouthCreek Originals, and Pizzas that are inspired by our friends who inspire us! Our beer and wine lists are complete with local and international selections available by the glass, carafe or bottle. We also have home made White and Red Sangria. With our open kitchen you can watch your Pizza baking in our Stephano Ferrara oven. We bake pizzas in about 90 seconds at 900 degrees!',history:'Established in 2013. We ( Mike and Linda Madan) have been involved with the pizza industry for many years in our DoughMate dough tray business servicing large and small pizza companies all over the world. We discovered how great wood fired pizzas can be while visiting our clients and during trips to Italy. We had a dream of recreating great Wood Fired Pizzas for our friends and family. While living in New Jersey we installed a wood fired oven on our patio, learned and practiced and had so much fun having pizza parties and tastings, that we started to dream about having our own restaurant and share the experience with more people. Our son Ian shared that dream as well. He started to make pizza at home in Truckee Ca. with super results. Ian gave up his job as a school administrator to work at Campo in Reno and hone his pizza making skills in preparation for running the kitchen at SouthCreek Pizza Co. SouthCreek Pizza Co. is the result of making dreams come true.....',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Sabrina\'s West Street Kitchen',website:'weststreetmarketreno.com/business/sabrinas-west-street-kitchen/',address:'138 West St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89501',phone:'(775) 683-9378',categories: ['Salad',' Sandwiches',' Tacos'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Closed","Tue":"Closed","Wed":"11:00 AM - 2:30 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 2:30 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 2:30 PM5:00 PM - 8:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Sun":"Closed"\}',about:'Family owned and operated. Fresh. Clean. Delicious.',history:'Established in 2017. We started this because we wanted to do what we love.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Bangkok Cuisine',website:'bangkokreno.com',address:'55 Mount Rose St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89509',phone:'(775) 322-0299',categories: ['Thai'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"Closed"\}',about:'Fine Thai food is our specialty and we have been voted the best Thai food restaurant in Reno, NV since 1998. Bangkok Cuisine restaurant uses the best selection of fresh produce, poultry, seafood and fine cuts of meat to please all of our customers’ satisfaction.',history:'Established in 1996. Bangkok Cuisine takes pride in serving excellent Thai cuisine and providing warm, friendly and cheerful service to everyone that comes in to any of our Bangkok restaurants. Bangkok Cuisine aims to please customers who come in who want a break from cooking, or want take-out. On Behalf of Bangkok Cuisine, our family and staff, we welcome you!',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Great Full Gardens - South',website:'greatfullgardens.com',address:'748 S Meadows Pkwy Unit A-14',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89521',phone:'(775) 324-2016',categories: ['American (New)',' Cafes',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"8:00 AM - 8:30 PM","Tue":"8:00 AM - 8:30 PM","Wed":"8:00 AM - 8:30 PM","Thu":"8:00 AM - 8:30 PM","Fri":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM"\}',about:'Great Full Gardens Cafe & Eatery features a wholesome menu for breakfast, lunch & dinner, full barista services, beer & wine in a casual full service environment. Our restaurant caters to both the people with specialized dietary needs, such as vegan, gluten-free or Paleo, as well as to the person just looking for great flavor and a menu that is unique and delicious! We are proud to support and feature many items from local vendors and farmers.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Smiling With Hope Pizza',website:'smilingwithhopepizza.com',address:'6135 Lakeside Dr Ste 101 Bartley Ranch',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89511',phone:'(775) 825-1070',categories: ['Pizza',' Italian'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Closed","Tue":"Closed","Wed":"4:00 PM - 8:00 PM","Thu":"11:30 AM - 8:00 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 8:00 PM","Sat":"11:30 AM - 8:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 5:00 PM"\}',about:'Good Neighbors Making NY Style Pizza',history:'Established in 2023. More information to follow!',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'PJ & Co Restaurant & Saloon',website:'pjandco.net',address:'1590 S Wells Ave',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89502',phone:'(775) 323-6366',categories: ['Breakfast & Brunch',' Diners',' Sports Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"7:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"7:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"7:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"7:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"7:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"8:00 AM - 4:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Burger Me!',website:'burgermeusa.com',address:'6280 Sharlands Ave Ste 101',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89523',phone:'(775) 737-9404',categories: ['Burgers',' Salad',' American (Traditional)'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Locally owned and operated Fresh.Real all natural meats and locally sourced fresh ingredients Beef, Chicken, Turkey, Bison, Lamb, Pork, Ahi, Veggie and more Highly rated house-made veggie burgers Gluten-free options available Fantastic regular and garlic fries, sweet potato fries and hand dipped onion rings Fresh salads and lots of veggie alternatives',history:'Established in 2008. We started our first Burger Me! in Truckee, California in 2008. Three years later we started Burger Me! in Reno, Nevada. Featured on Diners Drive-ins and Dives in July of 2010. Esquire\'s Best Burger of 2012',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'La Strada',website:'caesars.com',address:'345 N Virginia St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89501',phone:'(775) 348-3401',categories: ['Italian'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Homegrown Gastropub',website:'homegrowngastropub.com',address:'719 S Virginia St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89501',phone:'(775) 683-9989',categories: ['Gastropubs',' American (Traditional)',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'We specialize in Organic American Comfort Food.',history:'Established in 2017. We started the food truck April of 2017 and we\'ll be opening up our own storefront in August at 719 S Virginia St in MidTown! We\'re going to specialize in using organic ingredients for you all to enjoy in our from scratch cooking and hopefully create memorable experiences with our kind hospitality!',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Casa Grande Mexican Restaurant & Cantina',website:'casagranderestaurant.com',address:'1655 Robb Dr Ste 1',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89523',phone:'(775) 746-0123',categories: ['Mexican',' Bars',' Seafood'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Gold \'N Silver Inn',website:'goldnsilverreno.com',address:'790 W 4th St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89503',phone:'(775) 323-2696',categories: ['American (Traditional)',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Comfort Food'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"6:00 AM - 6:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"6:00 AM - 6:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"6:00 AM - 6:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"6:00 AM - 6:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"6:00 AM - 6:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"6:00 AM - 6:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"6:00 AM - 6:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Full breakfast, Lunch, and Dinner menu served 24 hours a day every day of the year. We serve everything from cold cereal to New York steaks with customer favorites being our Chicken Fried Steaks, our Burgers, our Wings, and our 24 Hour Breakfast Menu. All of our sauces and dressings are made right here on the premises from fresh ingredients. We try hard to avoid pre-made and packaged food service items that are so prevalent in today\'s restaurant business. We have 2 banquet rooms, and we offer ouside catering services for all occasions. Everything on our menu can be ordered to go anytime, - day or night',history:'Established in 1956. Originally opened in 1956, we take pride in being Reno\'s oldest Casual Dining Restaurant. The original building was about one half the size of the current building with remodels and expansions having taken place in 1964, 1976,1990, and 2000. We have a strong and loyal local clientele and value and appreciate our "regulars" as well as all new customers who may be visiting us for the first time. We hope you enjoy your visit and will come back again - many times! You can\'t call yourself a Reno local if you have never been to The Gold \'N Silver.',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Skipolini\'s Italian',website:'skipolinispizza.com',address:'13971 S Virginia St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89511',phone:'(775) 852-2200',categories: ['Pizza',' Italian',' Salad'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:30 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:30 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM"\}',about:'At Skipolini\'s, you are guaranteed delicious hand tossed pizza topped with the freshest ingredients. Not only known for the famous labor inducing Prego pizza, but also the lasagna and sangria are a must! We provide a great dining experience in all of our restaurants. We also taste great with our take out and delivery! So how about letting Skipolini\'s do the catering for your next event? We would be happy to!',user: User.find(2)},
  {name:'Atlantis Steakhouse',website:'atlantiscasino.com/dining/fine-dining/atlantis-steakhouse',address:'3800 S Virginia St',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89502',phone:'(775) 824-4430',categories: ['Steakhouses'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Closed","Tue":"Closed","Wed":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Capturing the cosmopolitan essence of Chicago to San Francisco, the Atlantis Steakhouse is impeccably styled with a design that melds contemporary elegance with classic comfort. Atlantis proudly serves Allen Brothers of Chicago meats, the nation\'s finest steaks. These wet-aged USDA prime cuts are the ultimate grade of beef, chosen for their superb quality, marbling and flavor.',user: User.find(2)},
