  {name:'KitzMo Sushi',website:'kitzmosushi.com',address:'3335 Kietzke Ln',city:'Reno',state:'NV',zipcode:'89502',phone:'(775) 826-6789',categories: ['Japanese',' Sushi Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Since 2012, KitzMo Sushi has been providing Northern Nevada with fresh and authentic all-you-can-eat sushi that satiates everyone\'s hunger. No matter what kind of roll or nigiri you get, we always use the freshest fish on the market with the tastiest ingredients. We offer to-go ordering and takeout out, too, so that you can enjoy your delicious sushi in the comfort of your home. Our team of expert chefs are devoted to preparing high-quality cuisine that exceeds all of your expectations, so you can trust you\'ll always get an exceptional meal when you come to Kitzmo. KitzMo Sushi provides the best and most affordable sushi in Reno Nevada.',history:'Established in 2012. A local business leader and self proclaimed foodie joins hands with two sushi chef brothers to create a sushi and bento experience Reno has yet to offer.',user: User.find(2)},
