  {name:'Yardbird',website:'runchickenrun.com/las-vegas',address:'3355 Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 297-6541',categories: ['Southern',' American (New)',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"9:30 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"9:30 AM - 11:00 PM"\}',about:'A modern take on comfort food means shared plates, craft cocktails, critically acclaimed fried chicken, and an ideal place for brunch or dinner.',history:'Established in 2015. In the heart of Miami, restaurateur John Kunkel, founder of 50 Eggs, Inc., focuses his unwavering passion for food and cooking a wide variety of cuisines into a diverse group of successful culinary concepts. In just under two decades, Kunkel has built 50 Eggs, Inc into an award winning restaurant group, demonstrating his talents with brand ideation, menu development and operational excellence for a broad range of hospitality concepts.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Gordon Ramsay Pub & Grill',website:'caesarspalace.com',address:'3570 S Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 731-7410',categories: ['Pubs',' British',' Fish & Chips'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"10:30 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"10:30 AM - 11:00 PM"\}',about:'Gordon Ramsay Pub & Grill is the neighborhood pub as conceptualized by the award-winning chef. The 290 seat restaurant is the most authentic English pub experience in Las Vegas, as only a native UK chef can provide.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Gangnam Asian BBQ Dining',website:'yelp.com/biz/gangnam-asian-bbq-dining-las-vegas-2',address:'4480 Paradise Rd Ste 600',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89169',phone:'(702) 802-5508',categories: ['Japanese',' Korean',' Barbeque'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Korean BBQ, Japanese BBQ, Kobe Beef GangNam is beautifully decorated Japanese Korean BBQ restaurant with delicious food in Vegas. Our mission is to exceed our customers\' expectations in all aspects of taste, service and atmosphere. We wish to serve you in the best possible way at Gangnam. We are putting a new spin on Asian BBQ! Here at Gangnam Asian BBQ we are offering Japanese BBQ known as Yakiniku. We also have Korean BBQ. All with delicious and fresh food to please the people of Las Vegas and the visitors of this great city. GangNam Asian BBQ is located in 4480 Paradise Rd, Las Vegas, NV. It\'s on Paradise and Harmon street right behind Hard Rock Hotel.',history:'Established in 2013.Chefs from Japan and Korea come out with this Japanese Korean BBQ Concept. Gangnam has traditional Korean dishes, Japanese Tapas, Certified Angus and Kobe Beef, Natural Chicken, and Natural Pork. BBQ at Gangnam is Tapa Style so that customers can experience different kinds of meat. Most of the BBQ is served fresh and customers enjoy cooking on their own table.',user: User.find(7)},
