  {name:'Gordon Ramsay Steak',website:'parislasvegas.com',address:'3655 S Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 946-4663',categories: ['Steakhouses',' American (New)'],price:'$$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"4:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Tue":"4:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Wed":"4:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Thu":"4:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Fri":"4:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Sat":"4:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Sun":"4:00 PM - 10:30 PM"\}',about:'Diners Choice Award 2022 - World Famous TV personality and accomplished chef Gordon Ramsay serves his famous dishes in an exceptional fine dining atmosphere. Chef Gordon Ramsay\'s cuts of prime beef are aged to perfection under a program directed by the fiery, internationally renowned chef and his culinary team. This posh Las Vegas steakhouse opened with a bang in 2012, where no detail is left untouched.',user: User.find(7)},
