  {name:'El Dorado Cantina - Las Vegas Strip',website:'eldoradocantina.com',address:'3025 Sammy Davis Jr Dr',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 722-2289',categories: ['Mexican',' Bars',' Latin American'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Open 24 hours","Tue":"Open 24 hours","Wed":"Open 24 hours","Thu":"Open 24 hours","Fri":"Open 24 hours","Sat":"Open 24 hours","Sun":"Open 24 hours"\}',about:'Award-winning authentic Mexican restaurant with an extensive food and beverage menu featuring organic, non-GMO ingredients in a contemporary setting.',history:'Established in 2014. Voted among the Top Restaurants in the U.S. by Yelp two years running and the Best Mexican Restaurant in Las Vegas in 2018 by the Las Vegas Review-Journal. El Dorado Cantina brings its guests an authentic Mexican experience of the highest standards. In an upscale environment, our patrons enjoy traditional dishes crafted from carefully-selected ingredients. We pride ourselves in serving high-end Mexican cuisine made with sustainable and natural products. We also have a wide range of vegetarian, vegan, and gluten-free options. We are open 24 hours a day, seven days a week including all major holidays. During our Happy Hour and Reverse Happy Hour, we offer food and drink specials at our well-stocked bar. With service and selections that are unmatched in Las Vegas, you\'ll feel like you are truly part of the El Dorado Cantina familia.',user: User.find(7)},
