  {name:'Gordon Ramsay Burger',website:'planethollywoodresort.com',address:'3667 S Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 785-5462',categories: ['Burgers',' Chicken Wings',' Hot Dogs'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Gordon Ramsay Burger breaks the mold of the traditional burger restaurant. Come try one of Chef Ramsay\'s burger creations at the Planet Hollywood Las Vegas.',history:'Established in 2012. The Gordon Ramsay Burger Las Vegas menu uses only the freshest, quality ingredients. Beef patties are cooked over an open flame fueled by hardwoods - the only restaurant on the Strip to use this method - creating a more complex and powerful flavor. A 30-foot-fire feature takes center stage at Gordon Ramsay Burger Las Vegas, within a vividly colored room that seats 200 people. The room has been designed with a stylish ambiance drawing on the energy of the casino and the nearby Miracle Mile shops.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Bouchon',website:'thomaskeller.com',address:'3355 Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 414-6200',categories: ['French'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"8:00 AM - 1:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"8:00 AM - 1:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"8:00 AM - 1:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"8:00 AM - 1:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Bouchon\'s quintessential bistro fare changes with the seasons, and though their presentation may change, some of Chef Keller\'s favorite dishes remain as fixtures on the menu throughout the year: roast chicken, steak frites, and croque madame, as well as an extensive raw bar. The restaurant\'s cuisine is complemented by an extensive, international wine list. Each day, additions to the menu are hand-written on blackboards throughout the restaurant. Bouchon in Las Vegas has received numerous accolades from both the culinary community and national press. The Las Vegas Review Journal awarded a four-star rating to Bouchon\'s cuisine while its breakfast is consistently highlighted as one of Vegas\'s best.',history:'Established in 2004. In 2004, Chef Thomas Keller brought his award-winning bistro cuisine to the city of Las Vegas with Bouchon at the Venetian Resort-Hotel-Casino. Located in the property\'s Venezia Tower, Bouchon at the Venetian\'s soaring interior space was designed by Adam D. Tihany, who recreated the original Bouchon\'s vibrant environment. The restaurant features a classic mosaic floor, a magnificent pewter bar, antique light fixtures and hand-painted murals by French artist Paulin Paris throughout.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Mr. Mamas Breakfast and Lunch',website:'mrmamaslv.com',address:'5693 S Jones Blvd Ste 106',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89118',phone:'(702) 220-9224',categories: ['Breakfast & Brunch',' American (Traditional)',' Burgers'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Tue":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Wed":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Thu":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Fri":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Sat":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Sun":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM"\}',about:'At Mr. Mamas Breakfast and Lunch, we think the best experiences are at the places that make you feel right at home. We want you to love where you are as much as what you\'ve ordered from our expansive menu, so our genuine and inviting team will make you feel like family from your first visit. With options like our Greek or California omelets and pancakes perfected by our pure maple syrup, we\'re sure to have a breakfast to brighten up any morning. Our mouth-watering meals don\'t stop there, though. Come by for lunch to dig into our flavorful burgers, wraps, and sandwiches, and try our popular chicken-fried steak and eggs or our biscuits and gravy. No matter what you get, one thing\'s for sure -- our place will put a smile on your face.',history:'Established in 2007. Inspired by a father\'s successful home-style restaurant business in Michigan, since 2007, Mr. Mamas Breakfast and Lunch believes the key to success is to make others feel like they\'re at home. Even after being in the restaurant business for generations, we believe in that same philosophy and strive to fulfill it everyday.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Guy Fieri\'s Vegas Kitchen',website:'thelinq.com',address:'3535 S Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 794-3139',categories: ['American (Traditional)',' Burgers',' Comfort Food'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"10:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Tue":"10:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Wed":"10:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Thu":"10:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Fri":"10:00 AM - 11:30 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 11:30 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 11:00 PM"\}',about:'Guy Fieri\'s first Las Vegas restaurant features a delicious blend of casual foods including an extensive variety of burgers, wings, tacos, small bites and shareable food items. Take a trip to Flavortown at Guy Fieri\'s Vegas Kitchen & Bar. The celebrity chef brings you his big, bold flavors and tasty twists on comfort food. Bring your appetite and get ready to dine on everything from a Tatted-Up Turkey Burger to Jack Daniels steak to a giant, over-the-top cheesecake dessert. Take in the view of the Vegas Strip from our 6,500 square-foot outdoor patio.',user: User.find(7)},
