  {name:'Echo & Rig',website:'echoandrig.com',address:'440 S Rampart Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89145',phone:'(702) 489-3525',categories: ['Steakhouses',' Butcher',' Tapas/Small Plates'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 3:00 PM,4:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 3:00 PM,4:00 PM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Butcher & Steakhouse',history:'Established in 2012. Sam Marvin introduces a pioneering new concept which will transform the long-held theories behind the steakhouse formula while simultaneously reintroducing the neighborhood butcher shop.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Giada',website:'thecromwell.com',address:'3595 S Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 777-3799',categories: ['Italian'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"4:30 PM - 9:45 PM","Tue":"4:30 PM - 9:45 PM","Wed":"4:30 PM - 9:45 PM","Thu":"4:30 PM - 9:45 PM","Fri":"9:00 AM - 2:30 PM,4:30 PM - 9:45 PM","Sat":"9:00 AM - 2:30 PM,4:30 PM - 9:45 PM","Sun":"9:00 AM - 2:30 PM,4:30 PM - 9:45 PM"\}',about:'Enjoy the famous dishes of Chef Giada De Laurentiis at her first restaurant. Dine on Italian cuisine with refreshing, Californian influences while you enjoy a wine selection that has earned "Wine Spectator\'s" 2019 Best of Award of Excellence. Only in Las Vegas. Only at The Cromwell.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Shang Artisan Noodle',website:'shangartisannoodle.com',address:'4983 W Flamingo Rd Ste A',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89103',phone:'(702) 888-3292',categories: ['Noodles',' Chinese'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Shang Artisan Noodle aims to both honor and elevate the Chinese culinary tradition of handmade noodles. With an emphasis on high quality ingredients, classic techniques, and thoughtful presentations, we want to delight our guests with an affordable meal that satisfies all of their senses. (Just because we are a fast casual concept doesn\'t mean we can\'t offer an exceptional experience.) Our concept may be rooted in the past, but our execution embraces contemporary tastes.',history:'Established in 2016. Shang Artisan Noodle is established in September, 2016.',user: User.find(7)},
