  {name:'Juan\'s Flaming Fajitas & Cantina - Tropicana',website:'juansflamingfajitas.com',address:'9640 W Tropicana Ste 101',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89147',phone:'(702) 960-0695',categories: ['Mexican',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"3:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'We specialize in traditional Mexican favorites like Chile Rellenos, Carnitas, Enchiladas de Mole. We also have a select list of Vegetarian items. A must try-- our delicious Flaming Fajitas. Chose from Steak, Chicken, Pork and Shrimp. And finish your meal with our great tasting Flan!',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Gäbi Coffee & Bakery',website:'gabicafe.com',address:'5808 Spring Mountain Rd Ste 104',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89146',phone:'(702) 331-1144',categories: ['Bakeries',' Coffee & Tea',' Sandwiches'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"8:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"8:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"8:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"8:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"8:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"8:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"8:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Exotic, but stylish. We serve craft coffee and artisan pastries. Enjoy exceptional quality in a warm and trendy atmosphere. Our savory items will be served until 9:00 PM. After 9:30 PM, our desserts and drinks will be served to-go until 10:00 PM.',history:'Established in 2018.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'888 Japanese BBQ',website:'888japanesebbq.net',address:'3550 S Decatur Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89103',phone:'(702) 476-5033',categories: ['Barbeque',' Japanese'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'888 Korean BBQ',website:'888-korean-bbq.com',address:'4215 Spring Mountain Rd B107',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89102',phone:'(702) 463-9993',categories: ['Korean',' Barbeque'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'888 is the All-You-Can-Eat Korean BBQ experience you don\'t want to miss. Come and enjoy selections of premium meat such as kobe beef, kurobuta pork, and delicious seafood. Vegetarians can enjoy a variety of all-you-can-eat choices as well, such as corn, mushrooms, soups, and more. Don\'t compromise quality for quantity ever again. Located in the heart of the Las Vegas Chinatown, come join us for this unforgettable all-you-can-eat experience!',history:'Established in 2018. 888 opened its doors in late 2018 and changed the Korean dining experience forever here in Las Vegas. 888 was the first to introduce the kurobuta sampler. The sampler holds eight bite-sized cuts of kurobuta pork, marinated in 8 unique, homemade sauces. Shortly after, 888 introduced its all-you-can-eat menu which features delicious selections such as kobe beef, beef carpaccio, seafood, and much more. Today, 888 continues to offer its impressive ayce menu at a high standard and is a pioneer at reinventing the way we experience and enjoy Korean BBQ.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'The Palace Station Oyster Bar',website:'palacestation.com/eat-and-drink/the-oyster-bar/',address:'2411 W Sahara Ave',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89102',phone:'(702) 367-2411',categories: ['Seafood',' Bars',' Cajun/Creole'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Open 24 hours","Tue":"Open 24 hours","Wed":"Open 24 hours","Thu":"Open 24 hours","Fri":"Open 24 hours","Sat":"Open 24 hours","Sun":"Open 24 hours"\}',about:'Voted one of the top 6 oyster bars in america by jaunted.com, at Palace Station\'s Oyster Bar, you\'ll enjoy fresh gumbos, pan roasts, chowders and more. Open 24/7, seven days a week, this is proudly one of the must-try dining destinations in Las Vegas.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Sushisamba - Las Vegas',website:'sushisamba.com',address:'3327 S Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 607-0700',categories: ['Asian Fusion',' Bars',' Sushi Bars'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:30 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:30 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'SUSHISAMBA celebrates the culture and cuisine of Japan, Brazil and Peru. Conveniently located in The Grand Canal Shoppes at The Palazzo in the Venetian the restaurant welcomes guests with a dramatic art installation, a three-dimensional illustration of swirling "ribbons" that explode from the center of the room, wrapping tables, and winding around the sushi bar and lounge. The stunning visual effect evokes a feeling of movement and dynamism anchored underneath the 16-foot ceiling of the main dining room. Our inventive culmination of Japanese, Brazilian and Peruvian cuisine offers limitless culinary creativity. From Japanese tempura and sushi, to Brazilian churrasco and moqueca, and Peruvian anticuchos and seviches, there\'s something for every palate. Known for our inventive cocktails, acclaimed sake and Japanese Whisky selection, and deep commitment to service, you can be rest assured that whatever the occasion you and your guests will enjoy an unforgettable experience.',history:'Established in 2008. Only at SUSHISAMBA will you find a unique blend of Japanese, Brazilian and Peruvian cuisine, music and design. SUSHISAMBA is born of the energy and spirit of these three distinct cultures; a tri-cultural coalition that took root in the early 20th century. Thousands of Japanese emigrants traveled to South America\'s fertile soil to cultivate coffee plantations and find their fortune. In bustling cities like Lima in Peru, and Sao Paulo in Brazil, the integration of Japanese, Brazilian and Peruvian cultures flourished. This cultural phenomenon launched a culinary coup. Hearty moquecas and colorful seviches found a place at the table along side simple miso soup and tender sashimi. SUSHISAMBA serves these traditional dishes, plus more inventive fare, including sashimi seviche, tuna tataki, and our south american beef maki roll. Beating at the heart of every SUSHISAMBA is a deep appreciation for enjoying life and celebrating with friends.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Mama Bird',website:'mamabirdsk.com',address:'10550 Southern Highlands Pkwy Ste 140',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89141',phone:'(702) 570-6135',categories: ['Southern',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Smokehouse'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Fried chicken, chicken sandwich, chicken n waffles, ribs, brisket, chicken wings, deviled eggs, breakfast, takeout, catering.',history:'Established in 2018. Opened July 18th 2018 in Southern Highlands. Small, local family owned and operated.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Pizza Rock',website:'pizzarocklasvegas.com',address:'201 N 3rd St',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89101',phone:'(702) 385-0838',categories: ['Pizza',' Sports Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'A Variety of Italian and American pizza styles, all cooked in one of the restaurant\'s four different ovens, including Neapolitan, Classic Italian, Classic American, Sicilian, Roman, and Gluten Free. Highlights include Gemignani\'s award-winning pizzas such as the Sicilian-style Burratina Di Margherita (Burrata cheese, cherry tomatoes tossed with basil, extra virgin olive oil and balsamic reduction), which won the Gold Cup Pizza Championships Leece, Italy; Napoletana-style Margherita (San Marzano tomatoes, Mozzarella Fior de Latte, basil, extra virgin olive oil and sea salt), which won the World Pizza Cup Naples, Italy; and Cal Italia (Asiago, Mozzarella, imported Gorgonzola, sweet fig preserve, Prosciutto di Parma, Parmigiano-Reggiano and balsamic reduction), which won the Gold Medal in Food Network Pizza Champions Challenge.',history:'Established in 2013. Tony Gemignani, 12-time World Pizza Champion, brings his unique concept, Pizza Rock, to Downtown Las Vegas. Pizza Rock features gourmet pizzas in a variety of styles, hand-crafted artisan cocktails and an extensive imported beer and wine list; all served up in an artistic and energetic atmosphere.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Shake Shack Las Vegas - NYNY',website:'shakeshack.com',address:'3790  S Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(725) 222-6730',categories: ['Burgers',' American (Traditional)',' Fast Food'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"10:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"10:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"10:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"10:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"10:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"10:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"10:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Shake Shack serves elevated versions of American classics using only the best ingredients. It\'s known for its delicious made-to-order Angus beef burgers, crispy chicken, hand-spun milkshakes, house-made lemonades, beer, wine, and more. With its high-quality food at a great value, warm hospitality, and a commitment to crafting uplifting experiences, Shake Shack quickly became a cult-brand with widespread appeal. Shake Shack\'s purpose is to Stand for Something Good®, from its premium ingredients and employee development, to its inspiring designs and deep community investment. Since the original Shack opened in 2004 in NYC\'s Madison Square Park, the company has expanded to more than 350 locations in 32 U.S. States and the District of Columbia, including more than 100 international locations across London, Hong Kong, Shanghai, Singapore, Mexico City, Istanbul, Dubai, Tokyo, Seoul and more.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Nacho Daddy Downtown',website:'nachodaddy.com',address:'113 N 4th St',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89101',phone:'(702) 778-7800',categories: ['American (New)',' Mexican',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"8:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"8:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"8:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"8:00 AM - 3:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"8:00 AM - 3:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"8:00 AM - 3:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"8:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Don\'t let our name fool you, we don\'t serve nachos...we serve the most insane gourmet nachos smothered in queso and salsa made fresh daily, and we guarantee you\'ll never find a dry chip! Nachos nach\'yo thing? No worries - we have something for everyone, including all day breakfast, tasty Mexican-American collisions, and a full vegan menu. Be sure to try our housemade specialty drinks, including our Best of Las Vegas "Daddy\'s Margarita", or if you\'re feeling brave we dare you to #getstung with our world famous Scorpion Shot as seen on Tanked and the Food Network.',history:'Established in 2013. Las Vegas born and raised since 2010, Nacho Daddy is a locally owned modern Mexican restaurant setting the industry standard for fighting children\'s hunger in the community while also serving honest food to our friends.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Monta Japanese Noodle House',website:'montaramen.com',address:'5030 Spring Mountain Rd Ste 6',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89146',phone:'(702) 367-4600',categories: ['Ramen',' Noodles'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 11:00 PM","Tue":"11:30 AM - 11:00 PM","Wed":"11:30 AM - 11:00 PM","Thu":"11:30 AM - 11:00 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:30 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:30 AM - 11:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Carson Kitchen',website:'carsonkitchen.com',address:'124 S 6th St Ste 100',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89101',phone:'(702) 473-9523',categories: ['American (New)',' Desserts',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:30 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Urban American modern comfort food, unique ingredients, burgers, flatbreads & other small plates in sleek digs with a rooftop patio.',history:'Established in 2014. Kerry Simon and Cory Harwel built Carson Kitchen and opened in June of 2014.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'STK Steakhouse',website:'stkhouse.com',address:'3708 S Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 698-7990',categories: ['Steakhouses',' American (New)',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"4:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Tue":"4:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Wed":"4:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Thu":"4:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Fri":"3:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"12:00 AM - 12:30 AM,9:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"12:00 AM - 12:30 AM,9:00 AM - 11:00 PM"\}',about:'STK artfully blends the modern steakhouse and a chic lounge into one, offering a dynamic, fine dining experience, with the superior quality of a traditional steak house. High-energy drinking and dining in the heart of Midtown.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Herbs & Rye',website:'herbsandrye.com',address:'3713 W Sahara Ave',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89102',phone:'(702) 982-8036',categories: ['Steakhouses',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:00 PM - 3:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"5:00 PM - 3:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"5:00 PM - 3:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"5:00 PM - 3:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"5:00 PM - 3:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"5:00 PM - 3:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"Closed"\}',about:'Specializing in the craft of the cocktail with all hand pressed juices a large selection of great spirits, House made bitters etc. These are just some of the few compliments to Help the barmen behind the stick at Herbs and Rye. Excellent Italian cuisine, Steaks, Chops and Tuscan Flatbread from the Kitchen at Herbs and Rye compliment the deep Burgandy red velvet Wallpaper and Old Vegas Ambiance.',history:'Established in 2009. An unpretentious gem that pays homage to classic cocktail culture Tucked inside an unsuspecting building on West Sahara Avenue, this relatively new addition to the scene mixes up a range of cocktails in a handsome, galley-like setting. Meanwhile, the adjacent parlor-like dining room takes bar food to the next level with a full Steak House menu. Herbs & Rye, 3713 W. Sahara Ave.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Egg Works',website:'theeggworks.com',address:'2490 E Sunset Rd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89120',phone:'(702) 873-3447',categories: ['Breakfast & Brunch',' American (Traditional)',' Burgers'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"6:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Tue":"6:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Wed":"6:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Thu":"6:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Fri":"6:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Sat":"6:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Sun":"6:00 AM - 3:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Buddy V\'s Ristorante',website:'venetianlasvegas.com/buddy-vs',address:'3327 S Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 607-2355',categories: ['Italian',' American (Traditional)',' Wine Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:30 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'The menu offers twists on Italian-American favorites, as well as Valastro family favorites like Sunday Gravy, Eggplant Parm, and Grandma\'s Meatballs. The renowned baker\'s restaurant, of course, also serves an impressive dessert selection including Cannoli, Nutella Cake, and Valastro\'s famous Lobster Tail Pastry.',history:'Established in 2014. Buddy Valastro, of TLC\'s Cake Boss, has brought his first restaurant to Las Vegas at The Venetian. Buddy V\'s Ristorante, a partnership with veteran restaurateurs Elizabeth Blau and Kim Canteenwalla, is inspired by Valastro\'s family gatherings. The menu offers twists on Italian-American favorites, as well as Valastro family favorites like Sunday Gravy, Steak Pizzaiola and Linguine. The renowned baker\'s restaurant, of course, also serves an impressive dessert selection including Cannoli, Nutella Cake, and Valastro\'s famous Lobster Tail Pastry. Sit on the patio for envious views of the Las Vegas strip.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Chubby Cattle',website:'chubbycattle.com',address:'3400 S Jones Blvd Ste 15',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89146',phone:'(702) 868-8808',categories: ['Hot Pot',' Chinese'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"5:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"5:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"5:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"12:00 PM - 11:45 PM","Sat":"12:00 PM - 11:45 PM","Sun":"12:00 PM - 11:45 PM"\}',about:'As a reformer of the traditional Mongolian cuisine, Chubby Cattle is the first restaurant in the world to combine a refrigerated, conveyer belt-based hotpot with the finest traditional hotpot from Asia. The goal of this innovation is to provide our customers with the healthiest way to enjoy our fresh platters.To achieve the standard that we aim for in our mission, Mr. Yang personally selects the finest beef related products from the state of California and Montana.',history:'Established in 2016. Chubby Cattle is looking to reform traditional Mongolian cuisine. The newest addition to Chinatown Las Vegas is the first restaurant in the world to combine refrigerated, conveyor belt-based hotpot with the finest traditional foods from Asia. The goal of this innovation is to provide their customers with the healthiest way to enjoy their fresh dishes. To achieve the standard that they aim for in their mission, the team personally selects the finest products direct from the farms. Chubby Cattle is partnered with Little Lamb Hot Pot, the international restaurant franchise that operates nearly 600 locations throughout the world and NXT Group, an international conglomerate group. Together they have created a first-of-its-kind modern restaurant.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'SkinnyFATS',website:'skinnyfats.com',address:'6261 Dean Martin Dr',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89118',phone:'(702) 979-9797',categories: ['American (New)',' Burgers',' Sandwiches'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'SkinnyFATS specializes in healthy and happy menu items that cater to a variety of dietary needs, while providing tasty and delicious meals and snacks that are out of this world. The menu is a melting pot of cultural favorites with thoughtful ingredients and savory flavors.',history:'Established in 2013. Started from the bottom now we here.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Lazy Dog Restaurant & Bar',website:'lazydogrestaurants.com',address:'6509 S Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89119',phone:'(702) 941-1920',categories: ['American (New)',' Comfort Food',' Burgers'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"9:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"9:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Lazy Dog serves handcrafted American food and drink with seasonally-inspired ingredients. When you walk in, you get a small mountain town vibe from the warm, caring service and the rustic social setting. It\'s a great place to get together with friends and family.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Gen Korean BBQ House',website:'genkoreanbbq.com',address:'1300 W Sunset Rd Ste 2920',city:'Henderson',state:'NV',zipcode:'89014',phone:'(702) 476-8559',categories: ['Korean',' Barbeque'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Juan\'s Flaming Fajitas & Cantina - Henderson',website:'juansflamingfajitas.com',address:'16 S Water St',city:'Henderson',state:'NV',zipcode:'89015',phone:'(702) 476-4647',categories: ['Mexican',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'We specialize in traditional Mexican favorites like Chile Rellenos, Carnitas, Enchiladas de Mole. We also have a select list of Vegetarian items. A must try-- our delicious Flaming Fajitas. Chose from Steak, Chicken, Pork and Shrimp. And finish your meal with our great tasting Flan!',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Tom’s Watch Bar',website:'tomswatchbar.com',address:'3790 Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 740-6766',categories: ['American (New)',' Sports Bars',' Gastropubs'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"8:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"8:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"8:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"8:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"8:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"8:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"8:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Tom\'s Watch Bar defines the ultimate sports watching entertainment experience! We promise All The Sports, All The Time. With our highly curated sports programming, we are the best place to watch NFL, NBA, NHL, WNBA, MLB, NCAA, MLS, World Sporting Events, and much more! Our central oversized "stadium" screen, surrounded by hundred of high-definition screens, provides 360° viewing, making every seat at Tom\'s the best seat in the house. Tom\'s is the perfect place for fans to cheer with other fans, follow their fantasy players and follow any sports bet. We can\'t wait to see you soon!',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Eat.',website:'eatdtlv.com',address:'707 Carson Ave',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89101',phone:'(702) 534-1515',categories: ['American (New)',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Tue":"Closed","Wed":"Closed","Thu":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Fri":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Sat":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Sun":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM"\}',about:'The most hotly-anticipated new eatery in downtown Las Vegas, eat is the culinary brainchild of professional chef, Natalie Young. With 20+ years experience under her toque, Chef Natalie is delighted to bring the skills she honed pleasing the palates of top chefs, critics and other discerning foodies home to her friends and neighbors. Located at the corner of Carson and 7th Streets, eat is perfectly poised to serve downtown\'s business and residential communities, as well as adventurous suburbanites, tourists and any and all hungry people. What will "Downtown\'s New Comfort-Cuisine Queen" be cookin\' up? Check the menu.',history:'Established in 2012. Eat is the culinary brainchild of professional chef, Natalie Young. With 20+ years of experience under her toque, Natalie has long dreamed of bringing the skills she honed pleasing the palates of refined foodies, chefs, and critics in some of the nation\'s most celebrated kitchens, home--literally. A longtime resident of Downtown Las Vegas, Natalie\'s vision for Eat is as distinct as she is: fine, fresh, soulful fare, served in an unpretentious, uplifting atmosphere.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Lotus of Siam',website:'lotusofsiamlv.com',address:'620 E Flamingo Rd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89119',phone:'(702) 735-3033',categories: ['Thai',' Seafood',' Wine Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"12:00 PM - 3:30 PM,5:30 PM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"4:30 PM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"4:30 PM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"4:30 PM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"12:00 PM - 3:30 PM,5:30 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"12:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"12:00 PM - 3:30 PM,5:30 PM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Northern Thai Cuisine in a personal, elegant manner.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Honey Salt',website:'honeysalt.com',address:'1031 S Rampart Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89145',phone:'(702) 445-6100',categories: ['American (New)'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Inspired by the countless meals we have shared in our own home with friends over the years, Honey Salt is a restaurant devoted to family, friends and community. We offer a farm-to-table inspired menu that balances the reality of living in the desert with the amazing ingredients regionally available for those willing to look a little harder.',history:'Established in 2012. Honey Salt is the vision of restaurateur Elizabeth Blau and her husband, chef Kim Canteenwalla. A very personal and intimate vision of the food they love in the city they love, Las Vegas.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Nora\'s Italian Cuisine',website:'norascuisine.com',address:'5780 W Flamingo Rd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89103',phone:'(702) 873-8990',categories: ['Italian',' Cocktail Bars',' Seafood'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"4:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Timeless Italian Cuisine, Pizza, Pasta, Steaks, Seafood, Cocktails, Catering',history:'Established in 1991. Gino and Nora opened Nora\'s Cuisine in 1991 with a modest seating capacity of 12. Over the years the restaurant has expanded and is now one of Las Vegas\' hottest restaurants, serving locals and guests from around the world. Nora and Gino have 3 sons (Giovanni, Claudio, Marcello) and 11 grandchildren that you might see working at or running around in the restaurant from time to time.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Dirt Dog - Las Vegas',website:'dirtdogla.com',address:'8390 S Rainbow Blvd Ste 100',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89139',phone:'(702) 550-4682',categories: ['Hot Dogs',' Desserts',' Mexican'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"10:30 AM - 10:30 PM","Tue":"10:30 AM - 10:30 PM","Wed":"10:30 AM - 10:30 PM","Thu":"10:30 AM - 10:30 PM","Fri":"10:30 AM - 11:30 PM","Sat":"10:30 AM - 11:30 PM","Sun":"10:30 AM - 11:30 PM"\}',about:'Bringing Los Angeles Street Food and the Official Hot Dog of Los Angeles to Las Vegas!',history:'Established in 2013. Born in Los Angeles, Dirt Dog is Los Angeles Street Food Cuisine and Culture Incarnate!',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Sushi Neko',website:'dragonfactories.com',address:'5115 W Spring Mountain Rd Ste 117',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89146',phone:'(702) 247-4241',categories: ['Sushi Bars',' Japanese'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Fast Service Clean Check Special order item (Included A.Y.C.E)',history:'Established in 2015. 2nd sushi bar in las vegas first one is Sakana Neko is second',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Eiffel Tower',website:'eiffeltowerrestaurant.com',address:'3655 Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 948-6937',categories: ['French',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 1:45 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 2:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Tom Colicchio\'s Craftsteak',website:'mgmgrand.com',address:'3799 Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 891-7318',categories: ['Steakhouses',' American (New)'],price:'$$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'5 time James Beard Award Winning Chef Tom Colicchio is emphatic when it comes to creating menu items that appeal to all lovers of fine food. Craftsteak redefines the concept of a steakhouse by focusing on beef sourced from the world\'s top ranchers and artisanal producers. Using only the finest ingredients from small family farms and other specialized venues, every dish bursts with flavor. While this famous steakhouse offers mainstays like Kobe beef, specialties also include salmon, lobster, and an ever changing list of farmer\'s market vegetables.',history:'Established in 2010. Owned by MGM Resorts International',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Lo-Lo\'s Chicken and Waffles',website:'loloschickenandwaffles.com',address:'325 Howard Hughes Pkwy',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89169',phone:'(702) 483-4311',categories: ['Soul Food',' Chicken Shop',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"10:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Tue":"10:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Wed":"10:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Thu":"10:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Fri":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"10:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 8:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Nabe Hotpot',website:'dragonfactories.com/nabe',address:'4545 Spring Mountain Rd Ste106',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89103',phone:'(702) 202-1631',categories: ['Hot Pot',' Buffets',' Asian Fusion'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'All you can eat Hot pot shabu shabu',history:'Established in 2018. 09.14 Grand Opening',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Hobak Korean BBQ',website:'hobakkoreanbbq.com',address:'5808 Spring Mountain Rd Ste 101',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89146',phone:'(702) 257-1526',categories: ['Korean',' Barbeque'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 10:30 PM","Tue":"11:30 AM - 10:30 PM","Wed":"11:30 AM - 10:30 PM","Thu":"11:30 AM - 10:30 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 10:30 PM","Sat":"11:30 AM - 10:30 PM","Sun":"11:30 AM - 10:30 PM"\}',about:'Hobak Family likes to concentrate on few menu items, serving only beef and pork and concentrating on the quality of the ingredients. Working under the motto, "sharing great things," we encourage groups to enjoy the charcoal and gas cooking experience. On the menu, Our 100% pure premium Black Angus Beef is USDA certified and approved. We dare you to resist the savory flavors and juicy tenderness that only the highest quality meat can bring. Experience that unforgettables taste of wet-aged beef, an advanced 21-days technique that helps maximize softness of each bite. Our 100% Premium Heritage Pork comes from farms hailed for their passion in raising their livestock humanely, free of antibiotic + hormones, and only fed 100% fresh vegetation. Premium Heritage Pork actually helps in maintaining health, lowering fat and cholesterol via omega-3 fatty acids. Our Heritage Pork is also high in Vitamin-D, which helps prevent the hardening of arteries. Most importantly, our Premium Heritage Pork tasets amazing - a taste you cannot find anywhere else.',history:'Established in 2009. Hobak Family Inc. (the "Hobak Family") is a successful Korean BBQ chains in Korea. Hobak Family is a successful Korean barbecue brand in South Korea and currently operates 16 corporate-operated store and 8 franchises under 9 different brands. The Hobak Family is known for quality food, great services and ambiance. It caters toward younger demographics and their family and it is well known amongst younger generation for food quality and inviting and exciting atmosphere. After a long plan to expand its operations in the US, Hobak Family and we, Hobak Family USA, Inc., successfully launched its first Hobak Korean BBQ US location in Las Vegas, NV. A few months later, Hobak Family, Inc. and we executed a brand licensing agreement to expand our operations throughout the US territories.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Broken Yolk Cafe',website:'thebrokenyolkcafe.com',address:'6805 S Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89119',phone:'(702) 617-9655',categories: ['Breakfast & Brunch',' Cafes',' American (Traditional)'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Tue":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Wed":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Thu":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Fri":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Sat":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Sun":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM"\}',about:'Broken Yolk was one of the first full-service restaurants to find success in breakfast and lunch--no dinner required. Reclaiming brunch from the special occasion category and making it a meal for every day, they were pioneers in a segment that continues to grow in popularity. Guests with flexible schedules have discovered the joys of daytime dining; trading the ubiquitous egg bites and plastic-wrapped muffins for freshly prepared, quality food and friendly full-service.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Firefly Tapas Kitchen & Bar',website:'fireflylv.com',address:'335 Hughes Center Dr',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89169',phone:'(702) 369-3971',categories: ['Tapas/Small Plates',' Tapas Bars',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"10:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Back in 2003, Firefly burst onto the Las Vegas scene with its irresistible Spanish tapas, paellas, and sangrias, and we\'ve been stealing hearts (and appetites) ever since. This humble abode has become the go-to restaurant for authentic tapas, specialty cocktails, and a lively atmosphere. Firefly has become an iconic Vegas destination, and there\'s no denying why – we\'ve got the recipe for a memorable night out! We\'re not just serving up insanely delicious Spanish cuisine; we\'re also a place for weary industry workers and foodies alike to kick back, let their hair down, and have a fantastic time. Our Spanish cuisine? Irresistible. Our service? Top-notch. Our ambiance? Oh, you better believe it\'s on point. We\'ve got the perfect blend of mouthwatering dishes, warm smiles, and a vibe that\'ll make you feel like a million bucks.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Top of the World',website:'topoftheworldlv.com',address:'2000 S Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89104',phone:'(702) 380-7711',categories: ['American (Traditional)',' Steakhouses'],price:'$$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"4:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Tue":"4:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Wed":"4:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Thu":"4:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Fri":"4:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"4:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"4:00 PM - 11:00 PM"\}',about:'Located more than 800 feet above Las Vegas at The STRAT Hotel, Casino & SkyPod, the award-winning Top of the World offers a dining experience like no other. This Las Vegas fine dining restaurant features culinary delights served in an elegant atmosphere with unparalleled views of the city as the restaurant revolves 360 degrees every 80 minutes.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Truffles N Bacon Cafe',website:'trufflesnbacon.com',address:'8872 S Eastern Ave Ste 100',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89123',phone:'(702) 503-1102',categories: ['American (New)',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"8:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Tue":"Closed","Wed":"Closed","Thu":"8:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Fri":"8:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Sat":"8:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Sun":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM"\}',about:'Serving our hungry patrons an array of delightful dishes that playfully walks the line between delicious American comfort food and adventurous gourmet fare. The current menu consists of breakfast items, a variety of mac n cheeses, salads, sandwiches, burgers and desserts. We have also expanded to include more breakfast, lunch and dinner options. Among the cafes\' must-try is TNB Signature Burger, served with crispy Mac N Cheese topping, sriracha mayo on a brioche bun, and a generous helping of the cafe\'s award-winning bacon jam. Try our freshly brewed Citrus Iced Tea or our refreshing Ube Horchata to match our buttermilk fried chicken with waffles and maple syrup.',history:'Established in 2014. Same Great Taste! Just a New Place! Come and Visit us at our New Location! Please visit our official website for any changes in our normal cafe hours due to events and outside functions.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Jjanga Steak & Sushi',website:'jjangalv.com',address:'6125 S Fort Apache Rd Ste 200',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89148',phone:'(702) 914-8821',categories: ['Sushi Bars',' Steakhouses',' Teppanyaki'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:30 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:30 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:30 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:30 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Jjanga Steak & Sushi is SW Vegas\' best spot for sushi and hibachi. Tables designed for large groups and parties. Now serving All You Can Eat sushi! Over 100 items on the menu! Home of the sushi burgers!',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Wahlburgers',website:'wahlburgers.com',address:'3635 Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 405-9090',categories: ['American (Traditional)',' Burgers'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"12:00 AM - 2:00 AM,8:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"12:00 AM - 2:00 AM,8:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"12:00 AM - 2:00 AM,8:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"12:00 AM - 2:00 AM,8:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"12:00 AM - 2:00 AM,8:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"12:00 AM - 4:00 AM,8:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"12:00 AM - 4:00 AM,8:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Located within the Grand Bazaar Shops, Wahlburgers Las Vegas offers guests a perfect stop to grab a burger, Sloppy Joe sandwich or a fresh Wahlbowl. Join us at the full bar, sit down and diner in at tables with our signature green chairs, or enjoy the sunshine out on the patio. You can also stop just down the street along the Vegas strip to grab a drink or some souvenier Wahlgear at our Wahlburgers kiosk.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Gordon Ramsay Fish & Chips',website:'thelinq.com',address:'3545 S Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 322-0529',categories: ['Comfort Food',' Seafood',' Fish & Chips'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'There\'s only one place in Las Vegas to get perfect fish and chips. Not surprisingly it comes from world-class chef and television star, Gordon Ramsay. The chef brings his take on the classic English street food to The LINQ Promenade for an excellent fast-casual meal, no reservations required.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Chayo Mexican Kitchen + Tequila Bar',website:'chayolv.com',address:'3545 S Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 691-3773',categories: ['Bars',' Mexican',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"8:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Tue":"8:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Wed":"8:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Thu":"8:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Fri":"8:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"8:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"8:00 AM - 11:00 PM"\}',about:'Chayo Mexican Kitchen + Tequila Bar introduces a new concept in Mexican dining, combining a DJ, a sexy mechanical bull, a vast tequila and cocktail selection and a blend of authentic and innovative Mexican fare. Located just steps away from the Las Vegas Strip with direct access from The LINQ Hotel & Casino, Chayo is situated near the beginning of The LINQ Promenade, which leads to the Las Vegas High Roller Observation Wheel, offering unobstructed views of north america\'s largest observation wheel. The expansive ground-level patio is framed by lush trees and leads to the main dining room with floor-to-ceiling glass doors that open up to create an indoor-outdoor space. Once inside, a custom-made, highly-stylized mechanical bull stands as Chayo\'s mascot and the centerpiece to the 12,000-square-foot room. Nicknamed "Chayo," the bull tempts guests to take tequila-fueled rides set to music by a DJ playing an eclectic party mix.',history:'Established in 2014. Chayo Mexican Kitchen + Tequila Bar opened on Wednesday, Jan. 1,2014, as one of the first venues at the much-anticipated Caesars Entertainment development, The LINQ.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'China Poblano',website:'chinapoblano.com',address:'3708 Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 698-7900',categories: ['Chinese',' Mexican'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:30 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:30 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Le Thai',website:'lethaivegas.com',address:'523 Fremont St',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89101',phone:'(702) 778-0888',categories: ['Thai',' Beer Gardens'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Le Thai is a trendy, intimate Thai eatery offering an eclectic mix of Thai street food with American influences. Located in Downtown Las Vegas, Le Thai is a dining experience that you won\'t forget! Our dishes are inspired by family recipes that have been passed down from generation to generation. We specialize in curries, noodles, stir-fry dishes, and more! Our traditional Thai menu, inspired by Chef Dan Coughlin\'s Thailand-born mom and grandma, showcases our famous 3 color curry (a blend of red, yellow and green curries), homemade Thai noodle soup, and our always fresh, signature waterfall sauce. Le Thai will also offers a daily-weekly special board, so make sure to ask about our off-the-menu creations! Le Thai features an 800 square foot beer garden and hosts performances by local DJs. Check our our late night menu, available Thursday thru Saturday. Our beer garden into the place to be for late night hungry bar hoppers on downtown Fremont Street!',history:'Established in 2011. Le Thai has been serving Las Vegas since 2011. Our mission to is share the flavors of Thailand by offering an eclectic mix of Thai street food in a trendy, intimate space. With over 5 years of success, we look forward to adding you to our growing history of happy customers!',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Slater\'s 50/50',website:'slaters5050.com',address:'467 E Silverado Ranch Blvd Ste 100',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89183',phone:'(702) 766-5050',categories: ['Burgers',' Sports Bars',' Desserts'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Slater\'s 50/50 Las Vegas brings together a unique combination of gourmet burgers and craft beer in an atmosphere honoring the local Las Vegas community. With its signature 50/50 burger, made half ground beef and half ground bacon, plus mega milkshakes, 50 craft beers on tap—including locally brewed favorites—and walls adorned with artwork created by locals craftsmen and artists; Slater’s 50/50 is not only providing delicious indulgence for all ages but also celebrating the true spirit of Las Vegas. Slater\'s 50/50 famous Whale Burger won Netflix’s “Fresh, Fried and Crispy” Season 1 Episode and is also the Best of Las Vegas Winner for “Best Family Friendly Restaurant” and “Best Sports Bar.',history:'Established in 2018. Slater\'s 50/50 Las Vegas is an locally owned and operated gourmet burger joint that was started by husband-and-wife team Andy Kao and Cindy Sun in 2018. With two locations located in opposite sides of Las Vegas, our mission is to bring you the best burgers with fresh ingredients and top notch craft beer selection while creating a warm dining atmosphere that allows diners to feel at home.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'John Mull\'s Meats & Road Kill Grill',website:'johnmullsmeats.com',address:'3730 Thom Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89130',phone:'(702) 645-1200',categories: ['Meat Shops',' Barbeque',' Butcher'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"9:00 AM - 6:00 PM","Tue":"9:00 AM - 6:00 PM","Wed":"9:00 AM - 6:00 PM","Thu":"9:00 AM - 6:00 PM","Fri":"9:00 AM - 6:00 PM","Sat":"9:00 AM - 6:00 PM","Sun":"Closed"\}',about:'John Mull\'s Meat & Road kill Grill is the Infamous Meat Market and BBQ grill in Las Vegas, Nevada. We are a BBQ restaurant and Butcher shop with a full game processing service. We have been featured in "Diners, Drive Ins & Dives". Great customer service and great prices. Our Butcher shop offers many choice cuts and we specialize in top-quality beef, pork, poultry, sausage, turkey, goat, lamb, fish, cheese, lunch meat, rubs, sauces and seasonings. Other specialties such as frog legs, and rabbit. Advanced orders for smoked Turkey. Come in and taste our ribs, pulled chicken, pulled pork, beef brisket, hot links, tri-tip, and burnt ends. Sides are potato salad, macaroni salad, cole slaw, macaroni & cheese, baked beans, string beans, collard greens and yams. Located just East of Rancho,off Gowan.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Yama Sushi',website:'yamasushilv.com',address:'1350 E Flamingo Rd Ste 18',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89119',phone:'(702) 696-0072',categories: ['Japanese',' Sushi Bars',' Buffets'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM"\}',about:'Started in the late 80\'s Yama Sushi has been a staple restaurant in Las Vegas. We have grown through the years with our community as one of the first locations to offer AYCE Sushi. Our chefs have created very special rolls through the years with our long-time customers. Some of these menu items are now just part of the AYCE sushi community because they are so popular. We offer the most creative rolls with the freshest fish at the lower prices available! Come drop by and experience Yama Sushi yourself!',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Therapy',website:'therapylv.com',address:'518 E Fremont St',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89101',phone:'(702) 912-1622',categories: ['Bars',' American (New)',' Dance Clubs'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:00 AM - 2:30 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:00 AM - 3:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:00 AM - 3:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:00 AM - 3:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Brunch, Lunch, Dinner, NightClub, Hookah Lounge and Private Events, Dj\'s 10 pm to late,Kitchen close at 2 am We are great for groups! Therapy has several tables that seat from 6 to 150 pp. Meet your family, friends, or colleagues and Sip, Savor, and Share delicious offerings. We specialize in delicious food in an upscale but comfortably casual setting. Sharable Social Plates and Classic dishes with urban twists Highlight our version of American Fusion! We have handcrafted cocktails, several Signature Drinks, and delicious Sangrias, plus several dozen beers from around the world available. After Dark, we transformed IN Therapy NightCLub and Hookah Lounge, our DJ\'s start at 10 pm until late, you can get late bites until 2 am. on the weekends we also have party Brunch with award winner brunch and great Dj\'s on Saturdays and Sundays But it\'s all about THE FOOD! Look for us on Food Paradise shows on the Travel Channel as they recently wrapped up filming episodes centered on our famous Red Velvet and Fried Chicken Waffles, along with Fried MacnCheese croquettes with bacon tomato jam and aioli sauce. Come in for Good Food, Good Drinks, and Good Friends at Therapy all at local pricing.',history:'Established in 2015. June 20th, 2015 Down town Las Vegas in the East Fremont Entertainment district',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Island Flavor',website:'islandflavor808.com',address:'8090 S Durango Dr Ste 103',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89113',phone:'(702) 876-2024',categories: ['Hawaiian',' Asian Fusion',' Poke'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 7:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 7:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 7:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Sun":"Closed"\}',about:'Take a bite out of the island life with delectable authentic Hawaiian food from Island Flavor in Las Vegas, NV. Their restaurant proudly serves the finest Big Island styled creations for individuals and families across the region. Experience their warm and inviting atmosphere that is filled with Hawaiian culture from floor to ceiling. Their friendly staff is dedicated to providing you with excellent customer service during every visit. The Hawaiian restaurant offers a large selection of delicious menu items. Take your time selecting from appetizers that include fresh-made Ahi Poke and pork Won Ton. Don\'t miss out on their tender oxtail soup and teriyaki chicken salad. Pair your meal with one of their mouthwatering sides, such as fried rice, sweet potatoes, and macaroni salad, for a meal you\'ll never forget. For your entrée, indulge your taste buds in roast pork or kalbi short ribs. Their talented chefs prepare extraordinary ribeye steaks, pork chops, and kalua pig dinners. Large groups can take advantage of their island flavor pans of Lomi Lomi salmon and Korean chicken. Island Flavor employs a committed staff who will exceed your expectations through personal customer service. Feel free to ask them any questions you may have regarding the menu, and count on them to make helpful suggestions for your meal. You can also sit back and enjoy their live music performances on Fridays and Saturdays...',history:'Established in 2008. ',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Capo\'s Restaurant & Speakeasy',website:'caposrestaurant.com',address:'5675 W Sahara Ave',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89146',phone:'(702) 364-2276',categories: ['Italian',' Steakhouses',' Speakeasies'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"4:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"4:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Welcome to Capo\'s Italian Restaurant & Speakeasy! Growing up with his family\'s Italian restaurants in Chicago and inspired by the mobster era, Nico Santucci created Capo\'s, a real "speakeasy" featuring actual Al Capone\'s Family Secret sauces on our "made-man" pastas. Capo\'s is the kind of place that could be your home away from home - smells of spices and homemade cooking fill the air, and we offer a vast menu of traditional family specialties passed down through generations and modern adaptations sure to tempt every palate -- even the most discriminating of gourmets! Our nearly dark dining room, bathed in deep, sexy red booths is both inviting and comfortable to create an exciting dining experience that won\'t soon be forgotten!',history:'Established in 1964. Proudly serving Las Vegas for decades!',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Hot N Juicy Crawfish',website:'hotnjuicycrawfish.com',address:'4810 Spring Mountain Rd Ste C & D',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89102',phone:'(702) 891-8889',categories: ['Seafood',' Cajun/Creole'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"12:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"12:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"12:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"12:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"12:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:30 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Serving only the Best in Seafood. Spicy. For some people it\'s their taste-buds doing the tango, for others it\'s watery eyes, but for Tim and Laina it\'s a personality trait. They are drawn to the passions of life, and this is what led them to Las Vegas and the inevitable birth of Hot\'N\'Juicy Crawfish. Both grew up loving seafood and fun. They made several trips to Vegas to enjoy the amazing culinary diversity and the non-stop entertainment that the city is so acclaimed for. But something was missing amongst all the glitz, glamour, and gambling: something that they could not live without... CRAWFISH. Not just any crawfish, but the kind of crawfish that will keep you awake at night thinking about when you can get some more, the kind that doesn\'t need pretense, special occasion, or utensils. That was the last straw, it was time to do something about it. Vegas hasn\'t been the same since and they haven\'t stopped there...',user: User.find(7)},
