  {name:'Javier\'s',website:'aria.com',address:'3730 Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89158',phone:'(866) 590-3637',categories: ['Mexican',' Bars'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Bringing a Southern California favorite to the Las Vegas Strip, Javier\'s is now open in the center of the Casino Floor. Javier\'s delivers a rich heritage of authentic Mexican cuisine along with hand-shaken margaritas and a high-energy ambiance to Las Vegas. Enjoy Baja specials including selections of seafood, beef, pork, chicken and vegetarian dishes both at the exquisite bar surrounded by dozens of the world\'s finest tequilas and in the main dining room featuring a chainsaw wood carving highlighting the Aztec civilization. Javier\'s in Las Vegas has the energy of your favorite Mexican restaurant with the high-end cuisine you expect from a dinner on The Strip.',history:'Established in 2010. Owned by MGM Resorts International',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Tacos El Gordo',website:'tacoselgordobc.com/locations',address:'1724 E Charleston Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89104',phone:'(702) 251-8226',categories: ['Tacos'],price:'$',hours:'\{"Mon":"10:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"10:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"10:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"10:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"10:00 AM - 4:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"10:00 AM - 4:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"10:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'We do well our tacos?',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Fogo de Chão Brazilian Steakhouse',website:'fogodechao.com',address:'360 E Flamingo Rd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89169',phone:'(702) 431-4500',categories: ['Brazilian',' Steakhouses'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 2:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:30 AM - 2:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:30 AM - 2:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:30 AM - 2:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 2:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Sat":"11:30 AM - 10:30 PM","Sun":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Fogo de Chão is an internationally-renowned steakhouse from Brazil that allows guests to discover what\'s next at every turn. Founded in Southern Brazil in 1979, Fogo elevates the centuries-old culinary art of churrasco - roasting high-quality cuts of meat over an open flame - into a cultural dining experience of discovery. Please join us in our dining room, in our more casual Bar Fogo, or bring the Fogo Experience to you with Fogo To-Go or Catering. Visit our website to make a reservation or place an order.',history:'Established in 1979. Fogo de Chao is a leading Brazilian steakhouse, or churrascaria, which has specialized in fire-roasting high-quality meats since 1979 utilizing the centuries-old Southern Brazilian cooking technique of churrasco.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Border Grill',website:'mandalaybay.com',address:'3950 S Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89119',phone:'(702) 632-7403',categories: ['Mexican',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Tapas/Small Plates'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'With two floors of al fresco patio dining and a beautiful outdoor bar, Border Grill is the perfect setting for sipping refreshing cocktails and savoring the vibrant flavors of Mexico - including tacos, enchiladas, and ceviche - while enjoying views of Mandalay Bay\'s beach and pool. Vegan, vegetarian, and gluten-free friendly options available.',history:'Established in 1999. Border Grill Mandalay Bay is co-chefs/owners Susan Feniger and Mary Sue Milliken\'s two-story destination restaurant overlooking the pool and adjacent to the convention center. Border Grill Mandalay Bay boasts dual-level patios, an outdoor bar, and the talents of acclaimed Vegas Executive chef Mike Minor, a Border Grill veteran. Welcoming guests for brunch, lunch, and dinner, Border Grill Mandalay Bay features three additional private dining spaces and the ability to combine spaces or choose a full buyout for occasions ranging from formal sit-down dinners and cocktail receptions to festive buffets.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'JINYA Ramen Bar - Flamingo',website:'jinya-ramenbar.com',address:'4860 W Flamingo Rd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89103',phone:'(702) 868-8877',categories: ['Ramen',' Tapas/Small Plates'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 11:00 PM","Tue":"11:30 AM - 11:00 PM","Wed":"11:30 AM - 11:00 PM","Thu":"11:30 AM - 11:00 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:30 AM - 11:30 PM"\}',about:'We\'re Crazy About Ramen! JINYA is known for its slow-cooked approach to ramen, made from broths simmered for 20 hours in-house. From its customizable menu to sleek interiors, JINYA Ramen Bar presents a contemporary Japanese dining ideal for lively social gatherings for all ages.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'A.Y.C.E Buffet',website:'palms.com/eat-and-drink',address:'4321 W Flamingo Rd Palms Casino Resort',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89103',phone:'(702) 942-7777',categories: ['Buffets'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"2:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"2:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"9:00 AM - 4:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"9:00 AM - 4:00 PM,5:00 PM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'A.Y.C.E., a celebration of All-You-Can-Eat is redefining the Vegas buffet. Worldly cuisine presented in an innovative, technique-focused fashion will be the signature of A.Y.C.E., which will host guests in an open food hall setting. A.Y.C.E. features from-scratch recipes and various cooking methods set across seven stations: The Greenery, The Hearth, The Roastery, World Pan, Smoke & Fire, Revival & Sweet & Light.',history:'Established in 2018. From the delicious seafood - including crab legs on Wednesday, Thursday, and Friday evenings- to our carving station and made-to-order pasta dishes, our award-winning team is serving more options for you to choose from in hopes you\'ll leave well-fed and ready for a round-trip back for more!',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'TAO Asian Bistro',website:'taolasvegas.com',address:'3377 S Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 388-8338',categories: ['Asian Fusion',' Lounges'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Tue":"5:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Wed":"5:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Thu":"5:00 PM - 11:30 PM","Fri":"5:00 PM - 11:30 PM","Sat":"5:00 PM - 11:30 PM","Sun":"5:00 PM - 10:30 PM"\}',about:'Conveniently located inside The Venetian Resort and Casino, TAO Restaurant is an unparalleled, pan-Asian restaurant in the heart of the Las Vegas Strip. Stepping into the space transports guests from Las Vegas into an Asian paradise complete with a Japanese Koi-filled infinity pool, lush silk draperies, and century-old stones to complete the incredible ambiance. Every table in the 400-seat, two-level dining area is placed under the watchful eyes of our 20-foot Buddha statue, whose presence ensures every guest departs feeling completely satisfied.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Hofbräuhaus Las Vegas',website:'hofbrauhauslasvegas.com',address:'4510 Paradise Rd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89169',phone:'(725) 266-7190',categories: ['German',' Beer Bar',' Comfort Food'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Hofbräuhaus Las Vegas is the first and only German beer hall and restaurant to call Las Vegas home. As an exact replica of the legendary Hofbräuhaus in Munich, Germany, we take great pride in giving you an experience as authentic and unforgettable as the 400-year-old original. From the traditional Beer Hall bursting with nightly live entertainment, to the tree-lined Beer Garden, everything has a bold touch of Bavaria you won\'t forget any time soon. Come see why it\'s Oktoberfest every day at our Haus! Also; don\'t forget to put your jersey on and come to our Haus for all the featured Soccer games shown in our Beer Garden. Bayern Munich, Euro Cup, World Cup and so much more. We are definitely a great destination for sports and soccer games.',history:'Established in 2004. Hofbräuhaus Las Vegas was established in 2004 as the only exact replica of the original Hofbräuhaus in Munich, Germany. In 2014 Hofbräuhaus Las Vegas celebrated 10 years in Sin City and Mayor Carolyn Goodman proclaimed January 31 "Hofbrauhaus Las Vegas Day."',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'LAVO Italian Restaurant - Las Vegas',website:'taogroup.com',address:'3325 S Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 791-1800',categories: ['Italian'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Tue":"5:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Wed":"5:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Thu":"5:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Fri":"5:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 3:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 3:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:30 PM"\}',about:'LAVO Located in The Palazzo® tower at The Venetian® Resort Las Vegas is the premier destination for delicious Italian fare, paired with hand-crafted cocktails set against an ambiance only the Las Vegas Strip can deliver. An expansive space that incorporates a lounge, dining room and an outdoor terrace overlooking the Las Vegas Strip, LAVO offers experiential dining ranging from a romantic date night for two to a buzzing gathering of great friends or colleagues.',user: User.find(7)},
  {name:'Maggiano\'s Little Italy',website:'maggianos.com',address:'3200 S Las Vegas Blvd',city:'Las Vegas',state:'NV',zipcode:'89109',phone:'(702) 732-2550',categories: ['Italian',' Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(7)},
