  {name:'Cien Agaves Tacos & Tequila - Old Town Scottsdale',website:'cienagaves.com',address:'7228 E 1st Ave',city:'Scottsdale',state:'AZ',zipcode:'85251',phone:'(480) 970-9002',categories: ['Mexican',' Venues & Event Spaces',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM"\}',about:'At Cien Agaves, our philosophy is simple: serve the freshest food and drinks, using the highest-quality ingredients made from scratch every day. Because when it comes to creating Old Town Scottsdale\'s best margaritas and tacos, we don\'t mess around. While our philosophy is simple, the experience at Cien Agaves is anything but ordinary. Our menu features authentic Mexican favorites, as well as our own specialty creations like the Grilled Ono Taco and Tinga Taco - a crispy corn tortilla stuffed with chipotle-marinated shredded chicken. We have 100 hand-selected premium tequilas and specialty margaritas that are prepared when ordered, never using bottled sweet and sour and always with fresh-squeezed limes. It\'s all served up in a casual, relaxing environment adorned with colorful Mexican-style artwork, rustic Mexican star lighting, two separate dining rooms, two bars and two patios for outside dining.',history:'Established in 2007. Cien Agaves Tacos & Tequila opened its doors in October of 2007. With a passion for great Mexican Cuisine the locally owned company is inspired by redesigning tradition. A company that found success by handcrafting each menu item, Cien Agaves has become beloved by Old Town Scottsdale and its community.',user: User.find(1)},
  {name:'Persian Room',website:'persianroom.com',address:'17040 N Scottsdale Rd Ste 102',city:'Scottsdale',state:'AZ',zipcode:'85255',phone:'(480) 614-1414',categories: ['Persian/Iranian'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:30 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:30 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM"\}',about:'Persian Room is renowned for offering superb, traditional Persian dishes in very generous portions. For 28 years it\'s owner has been wowing patrons in the Valley with his succulent kebabs. Guest favorites include hummus, skewered meat or seafood kebabs, fragrant basmati rice, rich & tangy Persian stews, spoon-tender lamb shanks, and so much more. A signature dish at Persian Room that aficionados regularly seek out is koobideh kebab; a marriage of super-finely ground beef, lamb or chicken, onion & spices, that is molded onto a sword-like skewer, then grilled to juice-dripping perfection. This eatery offers far more than the norm, boasting a large clay oven used to make warm, yeasty flat-breads brought to each table during dinner service. Besides reasonably priced, generous portioned fare, Persian Room offers an inviting banquet room that can be reserved for wedding or birthday parties, corporate events or social gatherings. Come, enjoy a true culinary adventure in Persian cuisine!',history:'Established in 1977. In 1977, owner Nasser Nikkhahmanesh opened his first Persian restaurant, Shish Kebab House, in the West Valley. Eventually, he followed that with the modest-sized Wine & Kebab in Scottsdale. Ultimately he built his vision for the perfect restaurant, Persian Room, which continues the now 28-year long legacy of enthralling Valley diners with the best in Persian cuisine.',user: User.find(1)},
  {name:'Cherryblossom Noodle Cafe',website:'cherryblossom-az.com',address:'914 E Camelback Rd',city:'Phoenix',state:'AZ',zipcode:'85014',phone:'(602) 248-9090',categories: ['Sushi Bars',' Noodles',' Ramen'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"Closed","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(1)},
  {name:'Carlsbad Tavern',website:'carlsbadtavern.com',address:'3313 N Hayden Rd',city:'Scottsdale',state:'AZ',zipcode:'85251',phone:'(480) 970-8164',categories: ['New Mexican Cuisine'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"10:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"10:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Welcome to the Bat Cave. When your taste buds are craving something with a little kick, stop by Carlsbad Tavern on Hayden Road. We present to you a cave-like atmosphere inside and great patio dining outside, with heaters in the winter and misters in the summer. We serve delicious New Mexican cuisine and have Happy Hour and Reverse happy hour daily. We serve all your favorite Mexican dishes with a modern flare.',history:'Established in 1995. The New Mexican Bat Cave theme started at the original location on Scottsdale Road & Osborn with bats, Mexican Movie Posters and Roswell memorabilia. However, upon the move to Hayden & Osborn in the Spring of 1998 the Bat Cave theme took on a new shape with the creation of the Guano Canal with a waterfall on the patio and the main dining room becoming The Bat Cave with a fountain. After 11 years of adding to the décor, Carlsbad has been transformed into a place all ages can be comfortable in a multitude of different environments to suit the whole family. The Daily Guano has doubled in selection size over the years and the consistency is unchanged. The pride and desire for excellence in the Kitchen and from the Service Staff has maintained the experience to be more than just a place to get a bite. You can always visit Carlsbad to be entertained as well as having the best grub on the planet.',user: User.find(1)},
  {name:'Ocotillo',website:'ocotillophx.com',address:'3243 N 3rd St',city:'Phoenix',state:'AZ',zipcode:'85012',phone:'(602) 687-9080',categories: ['American (New)',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Bars'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 3:30 PM,4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 3:30 PM"\}',about:'Ocotillo Restaurant is a casual dining destination located at the corner of Third Street and Flower in midtown Phoenix. The indoor/outdoor blends native desert flora with modern architecture. The inviting indoor space has a full service bar, dining room and a communal wine events area. Outdoors you will find several unique spaces including the chef\'s garden, the mesquite terrace, the beer garden, and Lucy\'s lawn. Ocotillo Restaurant invites you to enjoy some great food, a signature cocktail, a glass of wine, a craft beer and some live music.',history:'Established in 2015. Opened September 2015',user: User.find(1)},
  {name:'Snooze, an A.M. Eatery',website:'snoozeeatery.com',address:'15054 N Scottsdale Rd Ste 110',city:'Phoenix',state:'AZ',zipcode:'85254',phone:'(602) 830-8030',categories: ['American (Traditional)',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Tue":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Wed":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Thu":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Fri":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Sat":"6:30 AM - 4:00 PM","Sun":"6:30 AM - 4:00 PM"\}',about:'Most breakfast & brunch restaurants start with the same script: eggs, batter, coffee & a big ol\' griddle. We\'ve found scripts are a lot like pancakes, they\'re best when flipped, so we\'re always looking to turn the best breakfast classics upside-down & on their side. Stop by for delicious pancakes, french toast, benedicts, breakfast burritos, oatmeal, breakfast sandwiches, bacon & more. From paleo to vegetarian & vegan or dairy free & gluten free friendly, we\'ll happily accommodate food allergies & diets. We want each morning to feel like your weekend & happy hour rolled into one, so our restaurants feature a full bar with alcoholic beverages. From mimosas to bloody marys, margaritas & local craft beers, we\'ve got cocktails & brews covered.',user: User.find(1)},
