  {name:'Snooze, an A.M. Eatery',website:'snoozeeatery.com',address:'310 N Gilbert Rd',city:'Gilbert',state:'AZ',zipcode:'85234',phone:'(602) 704-1208',categories: ['Breakfast & Brunch',' American (Traditional)',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Tue":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Wed":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Thu":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Fri":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Sat":"6:30 AM - 4:00 PM","Sun":"6:30 AM - 4:00 PM"\}',about:'Most breakfast & brunch restaurants start with the same script: eggs, batter, coffee & a big ol\' griddle. We\'ve found scripts are a lot like pancakes, they\'re best when flipped, so we\'re always looking to turn the best breakfast classics upside-down & on their side. Stop by for delicious pancakes, french toast, benedicts, breakfast burritos, oatmeal, breakfast sandwiches, bacon & more. From paleo to vegetarian & vegan or dairy free & gluten free friendly, we\'ll happily accommodate food allergies & diets. We want each morning to feel like your weekend & happy hour rolled into one, so our restaurants feature a full bar with alcoholic beverages. From mimosas to bloody marys, margaritas & local craft beers, we\'ve got cocktails & brews covered.',user: User.find(1)},
  {name:'Maple & Ash',website:'mapleandash.com',address:'7135 E Camelback Rd Ste 130',city:'Scottsdale',state:'AZ',zipcode:'85251',phone:'(480) 400-8888',categories: ['Steakhouses',' Seafood',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"4:30 PM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 1:00 PM,5:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 1:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Join us for $2 oysters and $40 mini seafood towers at Tower Hour Monday - Friday | 5-6PM!',user: User.find(1)},
  {name:'Hash Kitchen Arcadia',website:'hashkitchen.com',address:'4315 E Indian School Rd',city:'Phoenix',state:'AZ',zipcode:'85018',phone:'(623) 324-2640',categories: ['Breakfast & Brunch',' Bars',' American (New)'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Tue":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Wed":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Thu":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Fri":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Sat":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Sun":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM"\}',about:'Hash Kitchen is a creative a.m. eatery with a DJ, glitter mimosas, AZ\'s largest Build-Your-Own Bloody Mary Bar and over-the-top exciting menu items that yield a social dining experience. Guests can expect to see cereal French toast, giant breakfast sandwiches, creative craft cocktails and bold savory dishes among other items. It is designed to be the go-to spot for locals and a culinary destination for visitors.',user: User.find(1)},
  {name:'Lou Malnati\'s Pizzeria',website:'loumalnatis.com',address:'100 E Camelback Rd Ste 152',city:'Phoenix',state:'AZ',zipcode:'85012',phone:'(602) 892-9998',categories: ['Pizza',' Italian'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(1)},
  {name:'Blanco Cocina + Cantina',website:'blancotacostequila.com',address:'6166 N Scottsdale Rd Ste 601',city:'Scottsdale',state:'AZ',zipcode:'85253',phone:'(480) 305-6692',categories: ['Tacos',' Cocktail Bars',' New Mexican Cuisine'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Blanco\'s fresh twist on Sonoran style Mexican food is all you need to satisfy every craving in Scottsdale. Lounge long and drink on with tantalizing tequila flights, delectable tacos, burritos, enchiladas, and the best margaritas you will ever drink. Whether you\'re hungry for something flavorful or thirsty for something fun, we\'ve got everything you want at Blanco.',user: User.find(1)},
  {name:'Welcome Diner',website:'welcomediner.net',address:'929 E Pierce St',city:'Phoenix',state:'AZ',zipcode:'85006',phone:'(602) 495-1111',categories: ['Diners'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Closed","Tue":"10:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"10:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"10:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"10:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"10:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"10:30 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'good food, good drinks, good times',user: User.find(1)},
  {name:'Topgolf',website:'topgolf.com',address:'9500 Talking Stick Way',city:'Scottsdale',state:'AZ',zipcode:'85256',phone:'(480) 240-2402',categories: ['Golf',' American (New)',' Sports Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"10:00 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"9:00 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"9:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'At Topgolf, our goal is to help you create unforgettable experiences with friends and family. Each venue features fun and competitive golf games for all ages, climate-controlled playing "bays" similar to a bowling lane, an impressive food and drink menu, full-service restaurant and bar, private spaces for groups of any size, HDTVs to watch the big game and a music selection that will make every visit feel like a party.',history:'Established in 2014. The story of Topgolf began on a driving range in 2000, where two brothers began brainstorming ways they could liven up their range experience and improve their golf skills at the same time. Fast forward to today, and Topgolf has evolved to become one of the most fun things to do in cities across the country. Complete with dynamic event spaces and a food and drink menu that would put any sports bar to shame, Topgolf is the perfect activity for any age, skill level or time of year. Its like drinks with your best buddies, a Sunday tee-time, social sports leagues with co-workers, a girls night out at your favorite restaurant, an arcade with the kids, and the best date night you\'ve ever had all rolled into one.',user: User.find(1)},
  {name:'Worth Takeaway',website:'worthtakeaway.com',address:'218 W Main St',city:'Mesa',state:'AZ',zipcode:'85201',phone:'(480) 833-2180',categories: ['Breakfast & Brunch',' Sandwiches',' American (New)'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Serving lunch and dinner all day, breakfast every day from 8:00-11:00am. Craft sandwiches made from locally sourced products, most items being made in house. Make any sandwich gluten free or Paleo by ordering it \'bowl style\' over greens with roasted sweet potatoes. Items that we are especially proud of; our Crispy Chicken Sandwich, house made pickles, banana pudding, house made chips and our cuban! Some of our partners include Noble Bread Bakery, Provision Coffee, Steadfast Farm, Stonegrindz Chocolate, and Simple Soda Co. Food lovers will appreciate the fresh ingredients we use. If you have an event, let us know, we have catering services as well.',history:'Established in 2016. Craft sandwich shop in the heart of downtown Mesa, bringing quality, local products to the neighborhood.',user: User.find(1)},
  {name:'Vovomeena',website:'vovomeena.com',address:'1515 N 7th Ave Ste 170',city:'Phoenix',state:'AZ',zipcode:'85007',phone:'(602) 252-2541',categories: ['Coffee & Tea',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"6:30 AM - 1:00 PM","Tue":"6:30 AM - 1:00 PM","Wed":"6:30 AM - 1:00 PM","Thu":"6:30 AM - 1:00 PM","Fri":"6:30 AM - 1:00 PM","Sat":"7:30 AM - 1:00 PM","Sun":"7:30 AM - 1:00 PM"\}',about:'we would like to be your morning go-to for coffee, breakfast, and brunch. we are a locally owned and operated, independent restaurant committed to offering some expected and extraordinary menu items.',history:'Established in 2012. portuguese slang for granmother + nickname for Ermenia = VOVOMEENA. an exeptional person, personality, cook, baker, and family leader. this is the kind of restaurant that is meant to make you feel comfortable. created by the folks that brought you Tuck Shop and Astor House.',user: User.find(1)},
  {name:'Pecan Lodge',website:'pecanlodge.com',address:'2702 Main St',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75226',phone:'(214) 748-8900',categories: ['Sandwiches',' Barbeque',' Southern'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Ellen\'s',website:'ellens.com',address:'1790 N Record St',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75202',phone:'(469) 206-3339',categories: ['Southern',' American (Traditional)',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Tue":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Wed":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Thu":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Fri":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Sat":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Sun":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM"\}',about:'Good old-fashioned southern comfort food and drink with a modern culinary twist. We have a barista and coffee bar for your favorite brewed beverages and a full bar for your adult beverages.',history:'Established in 2012. Ellen\'s believes that brunch is right, day or night. We serve brunch all day every day because it\'s brunch o\'clock somewhere!',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Maple Leaf Diner',website:'mldiner.com',address:'12817 Preston Rd Ste 129',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75230',phone:'(214) 434-1626',categories: ['American (Traditional)',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Diners'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"7:00 AM - 2:30 PM","Tue":"7:00 AM - 2:30 PM","Wed":"7:00 AM - 2:30 PM","Thu":"7:00 AM - 2:30 PM","Fri":"7:00 AM - 2:30 PM","Sat":"7:00 AM - 4:00 PM","Sun":"7:00 AM - 4:00 PM"\}',about:'Dallas\'s Original Canadian Diner featuring homestyle diner favourites and Canadian specialties like: poutine, butter tarts and Nanaimo bars. Featured on Food Network\'s Incredible Edible America, Travel Channel\'s Food Paradise, Paula Deen Magazine D Magazine\'s Best Breakfast Best of Dallas Advocate Magazine People Love Us on YELP Award Nextdoor - Neighborhood Favorite',history:'Established in 2015. We\'re bringing our slice of Canada to Dallas! Owner Michael Delaurier (an experienced restauranteur from Windsor, Ontario Canada) couldn\'t find food in his wife\'s Dallas hometown that felt like home hence he opened Maple Leaf Diner and brings a little slice of Canada to Dallas. Mike serves up traditional homemade diner delights like pot roast, burgers, chicken fried chicken and made-from-scratch pies as well as his homemade Canadian favourites like Poutine (fresh cut french fries topped with cheese curds and smothered in homemade gravy), PeaMeal Bacon (the REAL Canadian Bacon), Cabbage Rolls, Poutine, and Butter Tarts.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Kenny\'s Wood Fired Grill',website:'kennyswoodfiredgrill.com',address:'5000 Belt Line Rd Ste 775',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75254',phone:'(972) 392-9663',categories: ['American (Traditional)',' Steakhouses',' Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'We were just named one of yelps Top 100 places to eat in 2016! Thank you to all of you for helping make this happen! Upscale traditional American food like Filet Mignon & Crabcake, Tenderloin Crostini, Ahi Tuna Tacos, Shrimp, Crabcake, Caesar Salad, Ribs, Steaks, Pork Chops, Smoked Gouda Mac n Cheese, and Kenny\'s Famous Sterling Burgers. Great Martinis and a Full Service Premium Bar.',history:'Established in 2005. After 7 years of developing and building independent concepts and 6 years as a corporate chef, Kenny teamed up with friend and colleague Bob Stegall, a 20-year restaurant operator of both single and multi units. They created the very popular, upscale restaurant Kenny\'s Wood Fired Grill in Addison. Kenny\'s Wood Fired Grill has a comfortable private club atmosphere where chef Kenny Bowers creates the kind of food you wish you could make at home, with quality ingredients and attention to detail.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Ida Claire',website:'ida-claire.com',address:'5001 Belt Line Rd',city:'Addison',state:'TX',zipcode:'75254',phone:'(214) 377-8227',categories: ['Southern',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"9:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"9:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Ida Claire is a funky, southern influenced restaurant & bar. The food is notched up southern but has influences from different regions. You\'ll most likely see dishes you\'ve heard of before but with little twists here and there. Our sandwiches will be served on biscuits and we\'ll have chicken and waffles on every menu. Brunch is obviously southern and will be a big part of what we do. The drinks are takes on classics like the Mint Julep but revved up and including a lot of house made ingredients. We\'ll have several different house bitters and a house gin. The décor has a southern influence with antebellum charm and elegant polish, stated most clearly in our reworked air stream trailer parked in the garden for VIP reservations. The whole restaurant will feel like a quirky southern aristocrat\'s home...just not exactly what you might think.',history:'Established in 2015. Ida Claire opened its doors in 2015 with the aim of bringing an international spin on \'Southern Cuisine\'',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Gen Korean BBQ House',website:'genkoreanbbq.com',address:'2540 Old Denton Rd Ste 134',city:'Carrollton',state:'TX',zipcode:'75006',phone:'(469) 892-5669',categories: ['Korean',' Barbeque',' Asian Fusion'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM"\}',about:'Enjoy more than just delicious food. We\'re about the experience. Korean culture has taken the world by storm and at the forefront is the unapologetically bold Gen Korean BBQ House. With our vibrant atmosphere and menu based on authentic but modern Korean recipes, it is no surprise that people are willing to wait in line for over two hours just to get a taste of our All-You-Can-Eat (AYCE) KBBQ experience.',history:'Established in 2005. Gen first started in 2005 in Los Angeles, CA and have gradually expanded to the Phillipines, Hawaii, Texas and New York.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Meso Maya Comida y Copas',website:'mesomaya.com',address:'1611 Mckinney Ave',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75202',phone:'(214) 484-6555',categories: ['Mexican',' New Mexican Cuisine',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"10:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'A culinary adventure into the FRESH, BOLD and EARTHY flavors of authentic, interior Mexico.',user: User.find(3)},
