  {name:'Mike\'s Chicken',website:'mikeschicken.co',address:'4234 Maple Ave',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75219',phone:'(214) 443-7822',categories: ['Chicken Shop'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Sun":"Closed"\}',about:'Have you ever had tenders so juicy that they melted like butter in your mouth? We absolutely do tenders right just like that! We hand-cut tenderloins fresh daily, hand-battered them after we receive orders (nothing is pre-cooked), and cook them in 100% refined peanut oil. Don\'t forget to try our Mike\'s Buffalo sauce. "It will change you!"',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Whistle Britches - Dallas',website:'whistlebritcheschicken.com',address:'6110 Frankford Rd',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75252',phone:'(972) 590-8991',categories: ['Southern',' Beer Bar',' American (Traditional)'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 8:00 PM"\}',about:'Whistle Britches -chicken-biscuits-beer-',history:'Established in 2016. Chef Omar Flores and partner Alec Marshi established Whistle Britches in 2016. Located at Preston/Frankford in Dallas, TX specializing in chicken sandwiches, frozen custards and seasonal cocktails',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Maple and Motor',website:'mapleandmotor.com',address:'4810 Maple Ave',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75219',phone:'(214) 522-4400',categories: ['Burgers'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"10:45 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"10:45 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"10:45 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"10:45 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"10:45 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"10:45 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"10:45 AM - 4:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Jeng Chi Restaurant',website:'jengchirestaurant.com',address:'400 N Greenville Ave Ste 11',city:'Richardson',state:'TX',zipcode:'75081',phone:'(972) 669-9094',categories: ['Bakeries',' Chinese',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 8:30 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 8:30 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 8:30 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 8:30 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 8:30 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 8:30 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 8:30 PM"\}',about:'Jeng Chi opened its doors in 1990 with four tables and a small bakery. Dumplings and noodles were the fare then, Guests fell in love with the authentic Northern Chinese menu we were able to expand. Today, we\'re serving guests from a larger location in DFW Chinatown, one that hosts parties of up to 72 people (perfect for birthdays, anniversaries, and wedding rehearsals). Our menu has also grown, offering a range of dishes from Taiwan and Mainland China prepared by our highly skilled chefs. We even have a cafe and a full bar, both ready to serve you depending on your libation of choice. Jeng Chi is still a place for juicy dumplings, but it\'s also a place for connecting with others, a place to enjoy authentic food, and, most importantly, a place for our community to make memories in.',history:'Established in 1990. We originally opened in a small space in the same shopping center selling dough items. This family restaurant has expanded over the years to offer a menu of authentic dishes from Taiwan and Mainland China as well as a full bar and a relaxing cafe. No matter when you come by, you\'ll always feel right at home with something delicious in front of you.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'The Porch',website:'theporchrestaurant.com',address:'2912 N Henderson Ave',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75206',phone:'(214) 828-2916',categories: ['Southern',' American (New)',' Sandwiches'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"10:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"10:30 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Downhome Food. Uptown Cocktails. Lunch, dinner, weekend brunch.',history:'Established in 2007. The Porch is owned and operated by Raised Palate Restaurants and has been open since April, 2007.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Lazy Dog Restaurant & Bar',website:'lazydogrestaurants.com',address:'5100 Belt Line Rd St 500',city:'Addison',state:'TX',zipcode:'75254',phone:'(469) 754-1300',categories: ['American (New)',' Comfort Food',' Burgers'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Lazy Dog serves handcrafted American food and drink with seasonally-inspired ingredients. When you walk in, you get a small mountain town vibe from the warm, caring service and the rustic social setting. It\'s a great place to get together with friends and family. ',user: User.find(3)},
