  {name:'Oddfellows',website:'oddfellowsdallas.com',address:'316 W 7th St',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75208',phone:'(214) 944-5958',categories: ['Breakfast & Brunch',' American (Traditional)',' Diners'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"7:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"7:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"7:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"7:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"7:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"7:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"7:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Oddfellows offers an excellent happy hour seven days a week! Join us for indoor seating, patio dining, or take out! Thank you for supporting our small business!',history:'Established in 2010. Oddfellows was created by a collective of neighbors in the Bishop Arts District in Oak Cliff. Named Oddfellows for the wide array of career and personal paths the various partners have, the restaurant has a charming, welcoming vibe.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Kenny\'s Italian Kitchen',website:'kennysitalian.com',address:'5100 Belt Line Rd Ste 764',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75254',phone:'(972) 661-9380',categories: ['Italian'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"4:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Classic "Southern Italian American" food. Modeled after the Little Italy\'s of Boston, Philadelphia & New York. Classics like bone-in veal parmigiana, chicken parmigiana, meatballs, shrimp scampi, ravioli and more. Great martinis and a full-service premium bar.',history:'Established in 2010. After 7 years of developing and building independent concepts and 6 years as a corporate chef, Kenny teamed up with friend and colleague Bob Stegall, a 20-year restaurant operator of both single and multi units. They created the very popular, upscale restaurant Kenny\'s Wood Fired Grill in Addison. Kenny\'s Wood Fired Grill has a comfortable private club atmosphere where chef Kenny Bowers creates the kind of food you wish you could make at home, with quality ingredients and attention to detail. In December of 2008 after many requests for a burger place, Kenny & Bob opened the popular, Kenny\'s Burger Joint in Frisco.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Yolk - One Arts Plaza',website:'eatyolk.com',address:'1722 Routh St',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75201',phone:'(214) 855-9655',categories: ['Breakfast & Brunch',' American (Traditional)',' Coffee & Tea'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"7:00 AM - 2:30 PM","Tue":"7:00 AM - 2:30 PM","Wed":"7:00 AM - 2:30 PM","Thu":"7:00 AM - 2:30 PM","Fri":"7:00 AM - 2:30 PM","Sat":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Sun":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM"\}',about:'Great food, innovative dishes, premium coffee from the best local roasters, and fantastic service all delivered to you with a smile. That\'s the Yolk experience.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Twisted Root Burger',website:'twistedrootburgerco.com',address:'2615 Commerce St',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75226',phone:'(214) 741-7668',categories: ['Burgers',' Dive Bars',' American (Traditional)'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'With high-quality made-to-order burgers, a \'come as you are\' environment and a strange reverence for Chuck Norris, there\'s no place else quite like Twisted Root. Way back before \'gourmet burgers\' was a thing, Chefs Jason Boso & Quincy Hart decided to build a restaurant around half-pound, fresh ground burgers with a menu that allowed customers to build their own burgers with a list of crazy and inventive toppings. The two met in culinary school, after jobs in stock brokerages and telephone line repair. After paying their dues working the line at The Four Seasons & Pappas Bros, Jason & Quincy finally opened Twisted Root Burger Co. in the Deep Ellum neighborhood of Dallas, Texas in 2006. Twisted Root appeared on the second season of Diners, Drive-Ins, and Dives with Guy Fieri (2009) and suddenly Twisted Root was a dining destination in Dallas. While Twisted Root Burger Co. has seen incredible growth, Jason & Quincy have stuck to their roots and their senses of humor, using a hands-on approach to high-quality, fresh food in an casual atmosphere with tons of personality.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Yoshi Shabu Shabu',website:'yoshishabushabu.com',address:'1801 N Greenville Ave Ste 400',city:'Richardson',state:'TX',zipcode:'75081',phone:'(972) 807-9057',categories: ['Japanese',' Fondue',' Hot Pot'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Yoshi Shabu Shabu is the first of its kind to open its doors in DFW. At Yoshi, you are the chef!! All vegetables and produce come from local farms. Enjoy fresh delicately sliced meat or seafood, tofu, noodles, and assorted vegetables. All served with savory dipping sauces(original recipe from Osaka Japan), combined with fine imported Sakes, Beers, and Wines.',history:'Established in 2014. Shabu Shabu goes back a thousand years in the Japanese culture. At Yoshi Shabu Shabu we bring the real authentic Japanese version to the DFW area. We pride ourself in bringing the highest grade grass fed ribeye, Berkshire pork and sashimi grade Seafood to the table. All natural and hand picked. We have 68 years combined shabu shabu experience at Yoshi Shabu Shabu and plan to open many more stores in the near future.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Malai Kitchen',website:'malaikitchen.com',address:'3699 McKinney Ave Ste 319',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75204',phone:'(214) 599-7857',categories: ['Thai',' Vietnamese',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Thai & Vietnamese Cuisine made fresh in house daily including Spring Rolls, Fried Rice, Drunken Noodles, Iron Pot Green Curry with Chicken, and Grilled Tiger Prawns. Malai also offers over 90% of the menu Gluten-Free, Vegetarian or Vegan.',history:'Established in 2011. Led by husband-and-wife team Braden and Yasmin Wages, the concept was inspired by their extensive travels through Thailand and Vietnam. Our team is committed to sourcing quality ingredients and preparing as much as possible from scratch',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Taste Of Chicago',website:'tasteofchicagotx.com',address:'14833 Midway Rd',city:'Addison',state:'TX',zipcode:'75001',phone:'(972) 701-0090',categories: ['Pizza',' Italian',' Sandwiches'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"3:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"3:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"3:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"3:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"12:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"12:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"12:00 PM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'We specialize in the authentic Deep Dish Pizza and the italian beefs. We have variety of other selections on our menues that are very unique.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Beto & Son',website:'betoandsondallas.com',address:'3011 Gulden Ln 108',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75212',phone:'(469) 249-8590',categories: ['Mexican'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'If you\'re looking for delicious Mexican food in Dallas, made with local ingredients and a modern twist, stop by Beto & Son. Our Mexican restaurant provides a chef-to-table experience, with fresh flavors and meals made to order. From tacos and fajitas to our incredible frozen nitro margaritas, we have something for everyone. And, don\'t miss out on our new vegan menu. Stop in today!',history:'Established in 2016. Beto and Son opened November 16, 2016 in Trinity Groves.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Hopdoddy Burger Bar',website:'hopdoddy.com',address:'6030 Luther Ln Ste 100',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75225',phone:'(214) 363-2337',categories: ['Burgers',' American (New)',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Perry\'s Steakhouse & Grille - Park District',website:'perryssteakhouse.com',address:'2100 Olive St Ste 100',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75201',phone:'(469) 470-0622',categories: ['Steakhouses',' Seafood',' American (New)'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"10:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'In 1979, the Perry family opened its first restaurant: a modest meat market in Southeast Houston called Perry\'s Butcher Shop and Deli. By 1986, Chris Perry persuaded his father Bob to add dining tables, paving the way for an expansion and the opening of a second market. As the markets gained popularity, today operating as Perry & Sons Market & Grille, Chris went on to create Perry\'s Steakhouse & Grille in 1993. Now one of the country\'s premier, award-winning steakhouses with locations in Denver, Chicago, Birmingham and across Texas, Perry\'s remains true to its neighborhood butcher shop roots with top quality selection and service.',history:'Established in 2010. Perry\'s Steakhouse & Grille has earned a faithful following by perfecting prime since 1979. Beginning as a small butcher shop, Perry\'s has grown into a renowned group of award-winning restaurants featuring USDA Prime beef, tableside carvings, signature selections, flaming desserts and handcrafted cocktails at its Bar 79. Specializing in a Rare and Well Done® experience, Perry\'s currently operates steakhouse locations across Texas and in Birmingham, Chicago, Denver, Miami and Raleigh. Additional concepts include Perry & Sons Market & Grille and CARVE American Grille. For more information, please visit PerrysSteakhouse.com.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Uncle Uber\'s',website:'uncleubers.com',address:'2713 Commerce St',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75226',phone:'(214) 653-8237',categories: ['Sandwiches',' Burgers',' Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Uncle Uber\'s Sammich Shop in the Deep Ellum district in Dallas serves up fresh, hot griddled sandwiches to curb your hunger pains. But these aren\'t your typical cold deli sandwiches, we create sammiches, a term reserved for the holiest and mightiest of all sandwiches made with the best ingredients, the freshest ingredients... and basically, the right ingredients. Try our Shaved Ribeye Steak, The Cuban, or Smokin\' Turkey, and you\'ll know what makes a sammich unique! Foodies also love our Double Burger and hand-cut fries-if you’re in the mood for something simple. Wash down your grub with our regularly updated craft beers from local Dallas breweries, breweries from Austin, California, and Colorado, or we\'ll mix you up one of our un-crafty cocktails! Be sure to swing by on Wednesday nights for Trivia, or make our dive sandwich shop your game watching headquarters. We stress customer service and taking care of you and your sammich needs in a fun and artsy dive atmosphere. So whether you\'re taking a lunch break from the office, or grabbing a bite of dinner with the gang, let us be your neighborhood hang-out pick!',history:'Established in 2011. Uncle Uber\'s has been serving Dallas since 2011. Our mission is to delicious and unique sandwiches in a friendly and contemporary environment. With over 8 years of success, we look forward to adding you to our long history of happy customers.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Crushcraft Thai Eats',website:'crushcraftthai.com',address:'2688 LaClede St Ste 100',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75201',phone:'(972) 677-7038',categories: ['Thai',' Asian Fusion'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM"\}',about:'At crushcraft , we take integrity seriously every step of the way - from growing or locally sourcing our own basil leaves to hand-smashing our chili peppers. We are proud our Thai food is the real deal. Our core menu plus rotating items that we crave and coin Crew\'s Cravings, allow you to explore the staples of Bangkok and to push your palate with dishes you\'d rarely find outside Thailand. Come and enjoy amazing Thai Food and Asian Cuisine. Dishes with noodles, vegetables, chicken, meat, tofu, jasmine rice, Tom Kha soup, green papaya salad and appetizers. Cool down with local craft beer or sake. We are open late night. Daring but approachable, colorful and consistent - come by and experience crushcraft.',history:'Established in 2014. In the Spring of 2014, crushcraft opened as a small family fast causal restaurant looking to bring top notch ingredients, value, and the very best Thai food on planet Earth. crushcraft has quickly become a popular neighborhood eatery and awarded D Magazine\'s Top Ten Best Restaurant and featured on Food Network\'s hit show Diners, Drive-Ins, and Dives with celebrity Chef Guy Fieri. We\'re located in Uptown Dallas. Swing by for traditional favorites like our OG Phat Thai or our Phat Ke Mao aka Drunken Noodles. If you\'re feeling adventurous, we\'ve got staples not traditionally found like our Khao Soi...to even lighter fares like our Yum Gai Chicken Lettuce wraps. We even blend and crush fruit waters daily as well as serve local craft beers on tap so come on by and hang out on our patio!',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'The Boiling Crab',website:'theboilingcrab.com',address:'10560 Walnut St Ste 100',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75243',phone:'(972) 272-7086',categories: ['Cajun/Creole',' Seafood'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"3:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"3:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"3:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"3:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"3:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"12:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"12:00 PM - 10:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Amplified Live',website:'amplified-live.com',address:'10261 Technology Blvd E',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75220',phone:'(214) 350-1904',categories: ['Bars',' American (Traditional)',' Barbeque'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Closed","Tue":"Closed","Wed":"Closed","Thu":"Closed","Fri":"Closed","Sat":"12:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"12:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Amplified is a full service restaurant, bar, and music venue. We offer a one stop shop for some of the best food and entertainment between venues in the Dallas area. We have a diverse range of quality craft, import and domestic beers. Our barbecue has become an absolute guest favorite, all of our barbecue items are smoked in-house for an average of 13 hours! We have two stages, indoor and outdoor totaling in over 150,000 watts!! If you are looking for amazing food, fantastic service and the absolute best in entertainment in the Dallas area then look no further! Amplify your night life today!!',history:'Established in 2013. Formerly GMBG, this venue is not affiliated with Gas Monkey Garage, the Gas Monkey Brand or Richard Rawlings. Amplified, a full-service restaurant, bar and music venue! Packed with a state-of-the-art sound system, ample seating, and a menu comprised of Tex-Mex inspired roadhouse entrees, in-house smoked barbecue meats, and chef inspired craft burgers. There is no better destination in Dallas to enjoy some fantastic food, an ice cold beer, and catch any of your favorite bands!',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Empa Mundo',website:'empamundo.com',address:'3977 N Belt Line Rd',city:'Irving',state:'TX',zipcode:'75038',phone:'(972) 746-4516',categories: ['Latin American',' Argentine'],price:'$',hours:'\{"Mon":"10:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"10:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"10:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"10:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"10:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"10:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM"\}',about:'An empanada consists of filling inside of dough that has been folded, sealed, & cooked. At Empa Mundo our specialty is Argentinean empanadas, which we offer in more than a dozen delicious varieties. Here are some reasons why Empa Mundo empanadas are perfect for your family or events: They\'re versatile - They make a satisfying meal, snack or dessert at any time of the day, and have consistent flavor whether they\'re served hot or cold. They\'re a great timesaver - just as delicious when frozen, & then reheated. That means you can stock up, and have a FAST meal or snack on hand for your family anytime. Great for a picnic or any outing, no silverware or plates required. Ideal for a home or office get together - pick up several dozen. Also, mini empanadas make great hors devours. So many flavors, both meat and vegetarian options. Finally, they\'re delicious! Just ask any of our customers. We are so proud to bring this product to DFW and beyond, we know you\'re going to love them too.',history:'Established in 2010. Empamundo opened it\'s doors in January 2010, bringing a unique offering to the metroplex. Bonafide "stuff yer face" Argentinean style empanadas in close to a dozen different varieties. We are proud and excited to bring this delicious food to DFW, and look forward to meeting you!',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Andalous Mediterranean Grill',website:'andalousgrill.com',address:'6450 N Macarthur Blvd Ste 100',city:'Irving',state:'TX',zipcode:'75039',phone:'(972) 401-8900',categories: ['Mediterranean',' Greek',' Lebanese'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'The twins have brought a new twist to the old traditions with decadent dips, warm handmade bread, charcoal cooked kebabs, and tempting desserts. The diverse menu offers a variety of choices for any low calorie, low carb, or vegetarian diet.',history:'Established in 2012. Andalous Mediterranean Grill features delicious, flavorful cuisine from a variety of regions. Our family recipes include fresh fruits, vegetables, meat, seafood and poultry dishes. Enjoy a menu that is brimming with gourmet Mediterranean delights and contains many healthy entrées and salads. Our beautiful food line allows you to select your meal exactly the way you like it. Visit Andalous today.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Whiskey Cake',website:'whiskeycake.com',address:'3225 Regent Blvd',city:'Irving',state:'TX',zipcode:'75063',phone:'(469) 941-2253',categories: ['American (New)',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'We\'re serving up tasty farm-to-kitchen dishes & cocktails out of our from-scratch-only kitchen and bar. We use slow-cooking methods on our live-wood grill, smoker, and spit because food just tastes better that way. We believe that local is a place as much as it is a way of eating. Everything on our menu is infused with and inspired by the local ingredients available each season. All of this goodness is served to you as you kick your feet up in our rocking chairs, dine at a fancy table, or relax out on our porch.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Serious Pizza',website:'seriouspizza.com',address:'2807 Elm St',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75226',phone:'(469) 949-9234',categories: ['Pizza'],price:'$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:00 AM - 3:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:00 AM - 3:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'SERIOUS Pizza offers an over-the-top experience from the moment you walk in (or smell our pies from down the block). From the outrageously big slices and 30" pies you can hardly fit in your trunk, to the floating DJ booth and dough throwers in action, SERIOUS makes fresh NY-style pizza more than a meal, it\'s a vibe. Swing by solo for lunch or grab a late night slice with friends after a night out. When you\'re serious about pizza and a good time, go BIG!',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Fuel City - Dallas',website:'fuelcity.com',address:'801 S Riverfront Blvd',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75207',phone:'(214) 426-0011',categories: ['Convenience Stores',' Tacos',' Coffee & Tea'],price:'$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Open 24 hours","Tue":"Open 24 hours","Wed":"Open 24 hours","Thu":"Open 24 hours","Fri":"Open 24 hours","Sat":"Open 24 hours","Sun":"Open 24 hours"\}',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Pappas Bros. Steakhouse',website:'pappasbros.com',address:'10477 Lombardy Ln',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75220',phone:'(214) 366-2000',categories: ['Steakhouses',' American (Traditional)'],price:'$$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"Closed"\}',about:'Elegant, award-winning steakhouse serving dry-aged prime beef, seafood & exceptional wines.',history:'Established in 1976. H.D. Pappas left Greece in 1897 and traveled to America to pursue his dreams. He brought with him a passion for quality and service that became the benchmark of his success as he opened restaurants throughout Tennessee, Arkansas and Texas. It was this same dedication to quality & service that H.D. passed down to his sons and grandsons. His sons, Pete and Jim, chose a different path than their father and entered the restaurant equipment and supply business. They opened Pappas Refrigeration in 1945. Jim never dreamed that his sons would come full-circle by opening their first restaurant in 1976.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Kitchen + Kocktails',website:'kitchenkocktailsdallas.com',address:'1933 Elm St',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75201',phone:'(202) 998-6538',categories: ['Southern',' Comfort Food'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 11:00 PM"\}',about:'Global comfort fare like fried chicken & waffles, plus cocktails, served in a flashy lounge setting.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'The Woolworth',website:'thewoolworthdallas.com',address:'1520 Elm St Ste 201',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75204',phone:'(214) 814-0588',categories: ['Cocktail Bars',' Tapas/Small Plates',' American (New)'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Closed","Tue":"4:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"4:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"4:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"4:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"4:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"Closed"\}',about:'Unique culinary eats and creative twist on classic cocktails!',history:'Established in 2013. Downtown Dallas Neighborhood Secret',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Kirin Court Chinese Restaurant',website:'kirincourt.com',address:'221 W Polk St Ste 210',city:'Richardson',state:'TX',zipcode:'75081',phone:'(214) 575-8888',categories: ['Dim Sum',' Seafood'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 8:00 PM"\}',about:'Kirin Court offers some of the finest Chinese cuisine in Dallas. Indulge in our traditional dim sum prepared fresh daily. At Kirin Court, you\'ll find servers pushing carts through the dining room delivering tapas-size dishes of dumplings, pastries and rolls. " Top Ten Brunch - DFW Area" - Dallas Morning News',history:'Established in 2003. We started severing fresh Dim Sum daily since 2003.',user: User.find(3)},
