  {name:'CBD Provisions',website:'thejouledallas.com',address:'1530 Main St',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75201',phone:'(214) 261-4500',categories: ['Brasseries',' Beer',' Wine & Spirits'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"7:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"7:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"7:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"7:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"7:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"7:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"7:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Upscale Joule Hotel brasserie offers creative Texan comfort dishes & cocktails in a stylish setting.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Bistro B',website:'bistrob.com',address:'9780 Walnut St Ste 340',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75243',phone:'(214) 575-9885',categories: ['Vietnamese',' Asian Fusion',' Chinese'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"7:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"7:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"7:00 AM - 5:00 PM","Thu":"7:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"7:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Sun":"7:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Monkey King Noodle',website:'monkeykingnoodlecompany.com',address:'2933 Main St',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75226',phone:'(469) 713-2648',categories: ['Chinese',' Noodles'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'The Monkey King Noodle Company specializes in authentic Chinese street food, including hand-pulled noodles served with spicy beef or savory chicken broth, and handmade steamed goodies such as wontons, dumplings, and soup dumplings (xiao long bao).',history:'Established in 2013. The brainchild of owner and noodlemaker Andrew Chen, the Monkey King Noodle Company opened its doors in September 2013. Our grand opening is on Saturday, 11/15 at 6:00 pm. Come see us then as we launch our inaugural scheduled dinner service!',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Katy Trail Ice House',website:'katyicehouse.com',address:'3127 Routh St',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75201',phone:'(214) 468-0600',categories: ['Bars',' American (Traditional)',' Beer Gardens'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"10:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"10:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Best BBQ in town Thursday through Sunday.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Cris and John',website:'crisandjohn.com',address:'5555 Preston Oaks Rd Ste 5',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75254',phone:'(972) 803-4750',categories: ['Vietnamese',' Asian Fusion'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Closed","Tue":"11:00 AM - 8:30 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 8:30 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 8:30 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 8:30 PM","Sat":"Closed","Sun":"11:00 AM - 3:00 PM,5:00 PM - 8:00 PM"\}',about:'Stop by Cris and John where we bring Vietnamese Street Food like you\'ve never seen before! Our mission is to give you fresh and delicious food that fits your wallet #crisandjohn Follow us on Facebook @CrisandJohn and Instagram @crisandjohnvs.',history:'Established in 2017. \'Cris and John Vietnamese Street food\' was founded by Cristina and John. A young married couple with a passion for food. John, having grown up in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam, found his love for Vietnamese Street food at a very young age. His favorite thing to do was to walk to his favorite street food carts and sit and watch people as they buzzed by on their Vespa\'s. From the moment that Cris and John decided to open their own restaurant, they made it their goal to make their customers feel like they were stepping into the streets of Vietnam. Through their menu and decor, you\'ll definitely experience Vietnamese Street food like you never have before!',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Eno’s Pizza Tavern',website:'enospizza.com',address:'407 N Bishop Ave',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75208',phone:'(214) 943-9200',categories: ['Pizza',' Bars',' Italian'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:30 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Eno\'s pizza isn\'t NYC or Chicago style, but uniquely Dallas. Thin on the crust with room for fresh local ingredients. Whether you crave our original pizzas or homemade pasta, soup, sandwiches and salad, Eno\'s is open for lunch, dinner, and after hours. Grab a craft beer, hang out at our bar or enjoy the Texas weather year round on our outdoor patio. Want to skip the line? Eno\'s offers online delivery and pickup for convenience.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Snooze, an A.M. Eatery',website:'snoozeeatery.com',address:'5100 Belt Line Rd Ste 824',city:'Addison',state:'TX',zipcode:'75254',phone:'(469) 829-2232',categories: ['Breakfast & Brunch',' American (Traditional)',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Tue":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Wed":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Thu":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Fri":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Sat":"6:30 AM - 4:00 PM","Sun":"6:30 AM - 4:00 PM"\}',about:'Most breakfast & brunch restaurants start with the same script: eggs, batter, coffee & a big ol\' griddle. We\'ve found scripts are a lot like pancakes, they\'re best when flipped, so we\'re always looking to turn the best breakfast classics upside-down & on their side. Stop by for delicious pancakes, french toast, benedicts, breakfast burritos, oatmeal, breakfast sandwiches, bacon & more. From paleo to vegetarian & vegan or dairy free & gluten free friendly, we\'ll happily accommodate food allergies & diets. We want each morning to feel like your weekend & happy hour rolled into one, so our restaurants feature a full bar with alcoholic beverages. From mimosas to bloody marys, margaritas & local craft beers, we\'ve got cocktails & brews covered.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Afrah Restaurant',website:'afrah.com',address:'318 E Main St',city:'Richardson',state:'TX',zipcode:'75081',phone:'(972) 234-9898',categories: ['Mediterranean',' Lebanese'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"10:00 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"9:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"9:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Afrah is the Mediterranean Restaurant in Dallas, Richardson, Plano, Addison, Garland and surronding areas .Our food is a feast for the senses, famous for our Shawarma Pita sandwiches, fresh bread, pies and our homemade gelato and baklava. Featured in the Dallas Morning News and D Magazine, Afrah Mediterranean Restaurant dallas is the rich and exotic flavors of the Mediterranean in the casual comfort of our Richardson, Texas restaurant',history:'Established in 2002. Started as a pastry shop in February of 2002, our Mediterranean sweets became so popular that we decided to provide more of our family\'s Southern Lebanese recipes to our customers, evolving into the full service restaurant we are today. A family-run restaurant, the majority of our dishes evolved from our mother\'s recipes, prepared in house with Halal meats and the freshest ingredients. Afrah is one of the best mediterranean restaurant in Dallas, Plano, Allen and Richardson Texas.',user: User.find(3)},
