  {name:'Royal China Restaurant',website:'royalchinadallas.com',address:'6025 Royal Ln Ste 201',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75230',phone:'(214) 361-1771',categories: ['Szechuan',' Taiwanese'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 2:30 PM,4:30 PM - 9:30 PM","Wed":"4:30 PM - 2:30 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:00 AM - 2:30 PM,4:30 PM - 9:30 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 2:30 PM,4:30 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"4:30 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 2:30 PM,4:30 PM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Hand-pulled noodles and Hand made dumplings, Xiao-Long-Bao, Scallion Pancakes, Henan La Mian. The best dumpling in Dallas by Dallas Observer 2013. Good, healthy, Innovative new Chinese food and Authentic regional Chinese cuisine. Specialty teas like Oolong tea, chrysanthemum tea, lotus tea, fruit tea Dan Dan noodle is one of the 100 best food to eat in Dallas by D Magazine. Take out and delivery service.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'YO Ranch Steakhouse',website:'yoranchsteakhouse.com',address:'702 Ross Ave',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75202',phone:'(214) 744-3287',categories: ['Steakhouses',' Seafood',' American (Traditional)'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Hill Country-inspired fine dining featuring elk, bison & more in a Western ambiance with a patio.',history:'Established in 1996. The Y.O. Ranch Steakhouse claims its true Texas Heritage from the internationally known Y.O. Ranch in the beautiful Hill Country of the Lone Star State. This is obvious as soon as you walk in one of our several private dining rooms with authentic decor straight from the ranch.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Pluckers Wing Bar - Lovers & Greenville',website:'pluckers.com',address:'5500 Greenville Ave',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75205',phone:'(214) 363-9464',categories: ['Chicken Wings',' American (Traditional)',' Sports Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'STIRR',website:'stirrrestaurants.com',address:'2803 Main St Ste 110',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75226',phone:'(214) 983-1222',categories: ['Cocktail Bars',' American (New)',' Lounges'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"12:00 AM - 2:00 AM,11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"12:00 AM - 2:00 AM,10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"12:00 AM - 2:00 AM,10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'STIRR is a high energy, modern American restaurant and bar. The kitchen elevates classic dishes with unexpected twists to create a varied menu that offers something for everyone. Energetic bars anchor the space with bold and creative cocktails that enhance a great meal or stand strong on their own. Expansive rooftop patios offer great views and good vibes and are widely known as the best patios in town.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Vidorra',website:'vidorracocina.com',address:'2642 Main St',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75226',phone:'(972) 215-0640',categories: ['New Mexican Cuisine',' Mexican',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"12:00 AM - 2:00 AM,11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"12:00 AM - 2:00 AM,10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"12:00 AM - 2:00 AM,10:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Vidorra \'Cocina de Mexico\' is located in Deep Ellum celebrating Mexican food, drink and culture Meaning "the good life," the restaurant, patio and rooftop offers bold and exciting Mexican flavors, along with a large tequila selection, unique cocktail program, and lively social experience in one of Dallas\' most vibrant neighborhoods.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Blue Sushi Sake Grill',website:'bluesushisakegrill.com',address:'7859 Walnut Hill Ln Ste 180',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75230',phone:'(972) 677-7887',categories: ['Sushi Bars',' Japanese',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"12:00 PM - 9:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Al Biernat\'s',website:'albiernats.com',address:'4217 Oak Lawn Ave',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75219',phone:'(214) 219-2201',categories: ['Steakhouses',' Seafood',' American (Traditional)'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Al Biernat\'s is much more than a great steakhouse! Our menu rises above the traditional grill menu, with popular entrees such as Pan Seared Sea Bass over Lobster Risotto, Australian Cold Water Lobster Tail, Veal Osso Bucco, or Colorado Lamb Chops. The extensive wine list offers over 650 rare selections and a sommelier\'s expertise. Al Biernat personally greets you at the door to ensure your delightful dining experience. Come see why Al Biernat\'s is known as one of the best restaurants in the world',history:'Established in 1998. Al Biernat worked every front of house position available, including General Manager for 15 years at the Palm\'s Dallas location, before leaving to open his namesake haunt in June of 1998. Al Biernat\'s strong family-business philosophy has created a loyal staff in which most have been employed since the opening. The staff at Al Biernat\'s work with high regards to their knowledgeable employer, whom works by their side doing what he does best, being an excellent host.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Sushi Sake',website:'sushisake.info',address:'2150 N Collins Blvd',city:'Richardson',state:'TX',zipcode:'75080',phone:'(972) 470-0722',categories: ['Japanese',' Sushi Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 2:00 PM,5:30 PM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:30 AM - 2:00 PM,5:30 PM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:30 AM - 2:00 PM,5:30 PM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:30 AM - 2:00 PM,5:30 PM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 2:00 PM,5:30 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"5:30 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"Closed"\}',about:'Since 1997, Sushi Sake has been Richardson\'s premier sushi restaurant. One taste of our many delectable rolls and you\'ll be a fan for life! We\'re known for our excellent-quality food, in addition to our exceptional service and friendly staff. We offer over 15 raw and cooked rolls -- so whether it\'s your first time trying sushi or you\'re a sushi connoisseur, we have a roll that will delight your taste buds! Our customers love our entrees, like our delicious Ginger Pork and Amiyaki Beef. With delicious dine-in, and take-out options, we know we\'ll satisfy your cravings. Visit us today!',history:'Established in 1997. Sushi Sake has been serving Richardson since 1997. Our mission is to provide delicious food in a friendly environment. With over 19 years of success, we look forward to adding you to our long history of happy customers.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Thai Star',website:'thaistaraddison.com',address:'14833 Midway Rd Ste 100',city:'Addison',state:'TX',zipcode:'75001',phone:'(972) 991-6334',categories: ['Thai'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"Closed"\}',about:'We specialize in great Thai Food like , Pad Thai, Pad Ke Mow, Red Curry, Lemongrass Chicken, Spicy Beef, Hot N\' Spicy Stirfry, Homemade Dumplings, Grilled Satay, New Avocado Crab Fresh Roll, and Mango & Coconut Thai Kai, & not to forget my wife P\'or\'s yummy Tom Kha soup. When you enter Thai Star we treat you as we would our family. You are the only reason we are here. We sell Beer/Wine now and I have been working hard to find an unbelievable and tasty beer/wine list @ unbeatable prices. Our wines are delicious, affordable, and compliment our food! Come and check us out for beer and wine. Every Saturday, we feature local live Acoustic Singer Songwrwriter music. Our walls are filled with local artist\'s Art work. We support and try to help nurture local art. But make no mistake, our Thai Food is our true Star. Our lunch specials are $7.95 and are served with soup or salad, and spring roll. Lunch hours: Monday through Friday 11am to 3pm Take out & free delivery with no minimum.',history:'Established in 2010. We bought this Thai Restaurant in April 2010, where my wife had been the chef, for the past 5 years. We kept much of the same staff, but immediately change recipes to our liking. We put art, music, lighting, & a big TV inside the dining room. Over the next couple months we, upgraded, rewired, recovered, fixed & replaced broken parts, pieces, & all things in desperate need of love here. We introduced live music last July 10th on the eve of our official grand opening, & have done it every Saturday night. We do it for the love of music. We have been working on the beer & wine list. We have tried to deliver as promised, great tasting wines and domestic, import, and craft beers at very reasonable prices. Our one year anniversary party will be on Sunday July 3rd, we will open our doors @ 4pm, KaBoom Town, fireworks will be featured, we will have live music, outdoor Thai Barbeque, and all kinds of other surprises and fun. We are only OPEN for this one special Sunday.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Fortune House Chinese Cuisine',website:'fortunehousecuisine.com',address:'8150 N MacArthur Blvd Ste 190',city:'Irving',state:'TX',zipcode:'75063',phone:'(972) 831-9888',categories: ['Shanghainese'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 3:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 3:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 3:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 3:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 3:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 3:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 3:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Our Pastry Chefs carry on a special recipe: Traditional, Chinese Soup Dumplings. Steamed, is the most traditional way to go. You can\'t go to Fortune House and not order this dish. Bottom line is, we want you to see firsthand why our food is the best, and how passionate we are about our art. From our chefs and owners here at Fortune House, our family wants to thank each and everyone of you for making this dream a reality.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Mexican Sugar Las Colinas',website:'mexicansugarcocina.com',address:'3215 Regent Blvd',city:'Irving',state:'TX',zipcode:'75063',phone:'(469) 313-1300',categories: ['Latin American',' Mexican'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Paradiso',website:'paradisodallas.com',address:'308 N Bishop Ave',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75208',phone:'(214) 944-5865',categories: ['Bars',' Pizza',' Italian'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Coffee House Café',website:'coffeehousecafe.com',address:'6150 Frankford Rd',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75252',phone:'(972) 232-2333',categories: ['Cafes',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Tue":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Wed":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Thu":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Fri":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Sat":"8:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Sun":"8:00 AM - 3:00 PM"\}',about:'THE CAFE:Coffee House Cafe was created on the belief that an excellent coffee experience can make a daily routine divine. Our Espresso and House Blend are both 100% Certified Organic, Fair Trade and Shade Grown. THE COFFEE: Our coffee flavors are all house made with no preservatives, additives, high fructose corn syrup nor any other yucky scientific words that are too hard to pronounce. THE FOOD: With options such as the Chicken Apple Sausage Benedict with its perfectly poached egg and Chipotle Hollandaise or the Baja Seared Fish Tacos with a deliciously spicy Remoulade, we have got something for everyone.',history:'Established in 2011. Our Story We are excited to announce that Gilani\'s Family has aquired the Coffee House Cafe, a popular community eatery serving breakfast, lunch, and brunch. The acquisition was completed in August 2023. Before the purchase of the Coffee House Cafe, Allen Gilani and his family, along with other relatives, operated Cafe de France for 40 years in North Dallas and Plano. With the help of their dedicated employees, they achieved great success. However it will be challenging to replace Tonya Reese, who had a significant role in the Cafe\'s daily operation. as a longstanding member of this community and business, we strive to provide exceptional service and meals in this neighborhood and its surroundings. our dedication to listening and hard work has earned us a reputable resume. Our goal is to provide you with the same menu that you anticipate when you visit us for a meal and to give you the opportunity to interact with your preferred wait staff and hear your suggestions for new menu items',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Eatzi\'s Market & Bakery',website:'eatzis.com',address:'3403 Oak Lawn Ave',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75219',phone:'(214) 526-1515',categories: ['Bakeries',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Cafes'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"8:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Visit eatZi\'s and step inside our modern take on an old-world European market. From the incredible displays in our Chef Case to our made-to-order salads and sandwiches, you\'ll find a variety of fresh offerings as varied as the imaginations of our Chefs. Visit the Grill for a hot, ready-to-eat meal or explore our Chef\'s Corner for packaged meals made fresh daily. Then, when you\'re ready to indulge your sweet tooth, come to the Pastry Case where you\'ll find treats too good to resist! From breads to snacks, fresh fruit to flowers, cheeses, sides and the finest of wines, we have everything you need for gourmet-on-the-go. At eatZi\'s, holidays are always extraordinary with seasonal menus and limited-time offers. Visit our web site or stop by the market today and select Chef-crafted meals for your next special occasion and any day in between.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Happiest Hour',website:'happiesthourdallas.com',address:'2616 Olive St',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75201',phone:'(972) 528-0067',categories: ['Cocktail Bars',' Sports Bars',' Burgers'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"4:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"4:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"4:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"4:00 PM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"4:00 PM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"10:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Happiest Hour is one of Dallas\' most popular destinations with the largest patio bar and lounge, featuring a rooftop deck with an impeccable view and four full-service bars spread out over 12,000 square feet of indoor and outdoor bliss. The menu line-up that is sure to cure any craving and a giant beverage program featuring signature cocktails, wines on tap and more than 50 different beer selections. Happiest Hour is located at 2616 Olive St. in the Harwood District, mere steps away from the American Airlines Center in Dallas',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'The Henry',website:'thehenryrestaurant.com',address:'2301 Akard St Ste 250',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75201',phone:'(972) 677-9560',categories: ['American (New)',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Coffee & Tea'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"8:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"8:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"8:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"8:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"8:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"8:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"8:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Follow the arrow to the greatest neighborhood restaurant in Dallas, a place where you can always count on a warm welcome from baristas, servers and bartenders who know your order by heart. A fusion of industrial and classical influences, our open dining spaces are bursting with charm and energy. Come and go with ease for your morning coffee, enjoy lunch with a colleague, gather the family together for dinner, or treat yourself to a post-work drink at the bar. For craveable eats and downright delicious cocktails, look no further than a place where you\'ll always be among friends, a place that feels like home: The Henry.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Streets Fine Chicken',website:'streetsfinechicken.com',address:'3857 Cedar Springs Rd',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75219',phone:'(469) 917-7140',categories: ['Chicken Shop',' Comfort Food',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Taking on a Unique twist with Southern Texas food with a French Twist. Serving you delicious bites from Brunch, Lunch & Dinner Items, paired with fun & enjoyable cocktails.',history:'Established in 2016. We have been working on the concept for three years and waited to open it in the same location that made our family famous in the restaurant business. We are the founders of the Black Eyed Pea and this is the location of the very first one.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'LA Burger',website:'la-burger.com',address:'10045 N MacArthur Blvd Ste 113',city:'Irving',state:'TX',zipcode:'75063',phone:'(972) 501-9188',categories: ['Burgers',' Korean',' Tacos'],price:'$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"Closed"\}',about:'Korean-American Asian fusion. America\'s favorite foods from burgers, Asian style street tacos, sandwiches, salads, veggie options, infused with flavors from Korean, Mexican, Japanese, Chinese cuisine and more.',history:'Established in 2011. Inspired by the burgeoning Korean-Mexican fusion truck scene in their native Los Angeles, brothers Ben and Jon Lee found a perfect opportunity to pursue after their time in the Air Force. They opened LA Burger in Irving, TX to introduce diners to the flavors of Korean cuisine, fusing them with American favorites. LA Burger has received been featured in the Dallas Observer and D-Magazine while also receiving overwhelming praise on Yelp.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Fogo de Chão Brazilian Steakhouse',website:'fogodechao.com',address:'4300 Belt Line Rd',city:'Addison',state:'TX',zipcode:'75001',phone:'(972) 503-7300',categories: ['Brazilian',' Steakhouses'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 2:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:30 AM - 2:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:30 AM - 2:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:30 AM - 2:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 2:00 PM,5:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Sat":"11:30 AM - 10:30 PM","Sun":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Fogo de Chão is an internationally-renowned steakhouse from Brazil that allows guests to discover what\'s next at every turn. Founded in Southern Brazil in 1979, Fogo elevates the centuries-old culinary art of churrasco - roasting high-quality cuts of meat over an open flame - into a cultural dining experience of discovery. Please join us in our dining room, in our more casual Bar Fogo, or bring the Fogo Experience to you with Fogo To-Go or Catering. Visit our website to make a reservation or place an order.',history:'Established in 1979. Fogo de Chao is a leading Brazilian steakhouse, or churrascaria, which has specialized in fire-roasting high-quality meats since 1979 utilizing the centuries-old Southern Brazilian cooking technique of churrasco.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Ramen Hakata',website:'ramenhakata.com',address:'3720 Belt Line Rd Ste 3714',city:'Addison',state:'TX',zipcode:'75001',phone:'(972) 247-2401',categories: ['Ramen',' Vegetarian',' Seafood'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"12:00 PM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Ramen Hakata brings the top three styles of Japanese Ramen to the Dallas area. We feature a unique type of ramen otherwise known as Tonkotsu Ramen, which began in the Hakata district in the city of Fukuoka, Japan. Famous for the savory taste, the ramen features a rich broth, made by simmering high quality pork bones for at least 12 hours over high heat. This method of cooking releases bone marrow into the broth, giving the broth is milky white appearance and gelatinous characteristics. Our skinny ramen noodles are flown in fresh from California to accompany the rich broth with each bite. A variety of toppings such as Chashu pork, soft boiled egg, mushrooms, and more are prepared with care and are always of the highest quality. Come experience the beloved flavors of traditional ramen and see what the buzz is about at Ramen Hakata!',history:'Established in 2014. Ramen Hakata has been a new concept to Texas since 2014. Our mission is to bring authentic style ramen that\'s full of flavor and quality. Proud to be a part of our new community, we hope you\'ll join us soon at Ramen Hakata. Ramen Hakata has announced that the following store is coming soon. Address: 500 E Hwy 3040 in Lewisville Projected Opening: End- October 2016',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Keller\'s Drive-In',website:'kellers-drive-in.site',address:'6537 E Northwest Hwy',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75231',phone:'(214) 368-1209',categories: ['Burgers',' Sandwiches'],price:'$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:30 PM","Tue":"10:30 AM - 10:30 PM","Wed":"10:30 AM - 10:30 PM","Thu":"10:30 AM - 10:30 PM","Fri":"10:30 AM - 10:30 PM","Sat":"10:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"10:30 AM - 10:30 PM"\}',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Koryo Kalbi Korean BBQ',website:'eatkoryo.com',address:'2560 Royal Ln Ste 105',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75229',phone:'(214) 272-7486',categories: ['Korean'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Our menu features an extensive list of popular favorites as well as our own house specialties. come and relax with our attentive service and authentic Korean atmosphere. We have a variety of meats, soups and rice dishes to fit all tastes. Conveniently located in the North Dallas area. We present all kinds of traditional Korean BBQ and food. You can especially enjoy beef short ribs with home marinated with special house sauces. Previously known as Chosun Kalbi Korean BBQ, we have now changed our name to Koryo Kalbi Korean BBQ. Our high quality meals and service continue to be our first priority for you and our menu will stay the same.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'DaLat Vietnamese Restaurant & Bar',website:'dalatdallas.com',address:'2537 N Fitzhugh Ave',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75204',phone:'(214) 827-3200',categories: ['Vietnamese'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'We specialize in late night Vietnamese comfort food, including Pho and Banh Mi sandwiches. We have a fun and inventive menu that includes both authentic Vietnamese dishes along with creations that are Vietnamese cuisine inspired yet unique to DaLat. We will also endeavor to introduce Dallas to some traditional Vietnamese home cooking. These delicious and sometimes complex dishes are rarely found at other Vietnamese restaurants (anywhere in the world) due to their status within the Vietnamese community as "home cooking" and therefore not something that a Vietnamese person would normally order at a restaurant. Dalat also offers a full bar with an inventive menu of drinks and shots inspired by Vietnamese fruits and flavors. Our bar windows open completely to connect to an inviting and casual outdoor patio. We also welcome your Take Out orders.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'XOXO Dining Room',website:'xoxodallas.com',address:'3121 Ross Ave',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75204',phone:'(469) 397-4226',categories: ['American (New)'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"5:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"5:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"5:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"5:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"10:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"10:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Mr Max',website:'mrmaxtx.com',address:'3028 N Belt Line Rd',city:'Irving',state:'TX',zipcode:'75062',phone:'(972) 255-8889',categories: ['Sushi Bars',' Izakaya',' Ramen'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"Closed"\}',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Pie Tap Pizza Workshop + Bar',website:'pie-tap.com',address:'1212 Oak Lawn Ave Ste 131',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75207',phone:'(469) 677-0997',categories: ['Pizza',' Cocktail Bars',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'We are honest artisans who house craft with best available ingredients. Our food and drinks are created not made, and the end experience is an explosion of art and scent that results in edible, drinkable and lovable masterpieces.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Kona Grill',website:'konagrill.com',address:'8687 N Central Expy Ste 1722',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75225',phone:'(214) 369-7600',categories: ['Sushi Bars',' Bars',' American (Traditional)'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:00 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"10:00 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"10:00 AM - 11:00 PM"\}',about:'Kona Grill is a classic American grill featuring an array of delicious global menu items include hearty steaks and fresh seafood complemented by the best choice of sushi and cocktails in Dallas. From brunch and lunch to dinner and happy hour, we treat every guest to a diverse menu and a unique vibe dining experience in a polished, casual atmosphere. Our combination of upscale American cuisine, award-winning sushi, and a modern bar creates an innovative restaurant concept with something for every palate. Come visit us for brunch, lunch, dinner, or the best happy hour in Dallas!',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Dream Cafe',website:'dreamcafedallas.com',address:'2811 McKinney Ave',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75204',phone:'(214) 954-0486',categories: ['Breakfast & Brunch',' American (Traditional)',' Cafes'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Tue":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Wed":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Thu":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Fri":"7:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Sat":"8:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Sun":"8:00 AM - 3:00 PM"\}',about:'We are famous for breakfast. Along with our steel cut oatmeal, house made granola and whole wheat pancakes with pure maple syrup we have killer hash brown potatoes, eggs benedict and the best granola crusted french toast in Dallas, but don\'t just think of us for breakfast. We have a great outdoor patio and cozy, arty dining room and an electic menu. Hormone free burgers, melrose chicken club with carmelized onions and melted brie and asian pan seared salmon on our wasabi potato cake with honey soy glaze are just a few of the delicious choices. Laid back, Austin style has been used to describe us over the years, but "laid back" has been known to mean inattentive service and we are working overtime to out grow that moniker. We have a casual, friendly atmosphere and we strive to make each of our guests happy. So come in and order some great food in a laid back enviornment with some killer service, you\'ll be glad you did.',history:'Established in 1985. We are a Dallas institution! We started with six tables in a store front on Knox Street and after Liz Logan featured us in D Magazine we were on the map. We outgrew our little place on Knox and moved to the Quadrangle in January 1988 where we continue to strive to provide great food at an affordable price served by people who care.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Mia\'s Tex-Mex Restaurant',website:'miastexmex.com',address:'4334 Lemmon Ave',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75219',phone:'(214) 526-1020',categories: ['Tex-Mex'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:30 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:30 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:30 PM"\}',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Truluck\'s Ocean\'s Finest Seafood & Crab',website:'trulucks.com',address:'2401 McKinney Ave',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75201',phone:'(214) 220-2401',categories: ['Steakhouses',' Seafood',' Venues & Event Spaces'],price:'$$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Our chefs’ honor and elevate seafood dishes with superior ingredients, precise execution, and classic presentation. We are committed to serving the ocean’s finest seafood, fresh Florida Stone crab, and creating memorable moments nightly for our guests. Your table is waiting.',history:'Established in 1992. Founded in 1992 and fiercely independent since. Truluck\'s is proud to be a member of the Dallas community since July 1998.Located in the vibrant Uptown neighborhood at the corner of Maple and McKinney Avenues, Truluck\'s Dallas sits just north of downtown, blocks from the Museum District and American Airlines Center, and a short drive from Love Field.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Shell Shack',website:'shellshack.com',address:'6770 Abrams Rd Ste 180',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75231',phone:'(844) 588-2722',categories: ['Seafood',' Sports Bars',' American (Traditional)'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Shell Shack is your go-to neighborhood seafood restaurant offering the finest quality seafood and crab boils in town. Our precise and focused menu features a variety of boils, including King Crab, Snow Crab, Dungeness Crab and seasonal Bairdi Crab. Each is flavored to your liking with specialty seasoning options like Cajun. But be sure to try our "Kitchen Sink" house blend, which is a wet marinade that combines all flavors with your preferred heat level--try Hot or Diablo for a spicy kick. Our favorite seasonal boil is Crawfish with Corn and Potatoes. Other crowd favorites include Grilled Shrimp, Calamari, Oysters, Gumbo and Fried Catfish. We also offer "Stuff That Doesn\'t Swim" like fresh Burgers, Grilled Chicken, Chicken Wings, French Fries and Salads. Our kitchen is open until 1am for late-night food, and our full bar serves delicious drinks until 2am every day of the week. So let us cook and clean up the mess; you just come and enjoy Shell Shack for lunch or dinner today!',history:'Established in 2013. Shell Shack first opened in October 2013. Owners Dallas and Matt were inspired to create a restaurant that did things the right way -- provided great food and service. When the opportunity came, they took it and opened up the restaurant.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Grand Lux Cafe - Dallas',website:'grandluxcafe.com',address:'13420 N Dallas Pkwy',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75240',phone:'(972) 385-3114',categories: ['Desserts',' American (Traditional)'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'A world of food awaits at Grand Lux Cafe featuring internationally inspired cuisine.Located on the north side of Galleria Dallas facing the North Dallas Tollway and next to the Westin Galleria Hotel.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Hugo\'s Invitados',website:'hugosinvitados.com',address:'5240 N OConnor Blvd Ste 160',city:'Irving',state:'TX',zipcode:'75039',phone:'(214) 496-0590',categories: ['Seafood',' Cocktail Bars',' Mexican'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'At Hugo\'s Invitados, we carefully handcraft everything from scratch, and use only the most natural, wholesome, delicious ingredients possible. Our Mexican-inspired fresh cuisine and craft cocktails are unique, flavorful, and original. We make everything fresh in house daily - no fryers, no cans, no compromises. Come taste and see for yourself the Hugo\'s difference. Great food, service, and experiences worth celebrating. Hugo\'s Invitados. Celebrate every day.',history:'Established in 2018. Our grand opening: October 1st, 2018.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Omi Korean Grill & Bar',website:'omikoreanbbq.com',address:'2625 Old Denton Rd Ste 326',city:'Carrollton',state:'TX',zipcode:'75007',phone:'(972) 245-3565',categories: ['Korean',' Barbeque',' Seafood'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"12:00 PM - 9:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'E Bar Tex-Mex',website:'ebartexmex.com',address:'1901 N Haskell Ave Ste 120',city:'Dallas',state:'TX',zipcode:'75204',phone:'(214) 824-3227',categories: ['Mexican',' Tex-Mex',' Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:00 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:00 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:00 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'E Bar Tex Mex is a new trendy Uptown Dallas Restaurant serving amazing traditional Tex Mex as well as Beer, Wine, and cocktails. Join us for margaritas on the patio during Happy Hour or order delivery and get great food at your doorstep! Ask about our catering and private parties.',user: User.find(3)},
  {name:'Snooze, an A.M. Eatery',website:'snoozeeatery.com',address:'2262 Larimer St',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80205',phone:'(720) 792-2767',categories: ['Breakfast & Brunch',' Cocktail Bars',' American (Traditional)'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Tue":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Wed":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Thu":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Fri":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Sat":"6:30 AM - 4:00 PM","Sun":"6:30 AM - 4:00 PM"\}',about:'Most breakfast & brunch restaurants start with the same script: eggs, batter, coffee & a big ol\' griddle. We\'ve found scripts are a lot like pancakes, they\'re best when flipped, so we\'re always looking to turn the best breakfast classics upside-down & on their side. Stop by for delicious pancakes, french toast, benedicts, breakfast burritos, oatmeal, breakfast sandwiches, bacon & more. From paleo to vegetarian & vegan or dairy free & gluten free friendly, we\'ll happily accommodate food allergies & diets. We want each morning to feel like your weekend & happy hour rolled into one, so our restaurants feature a full bar with alcoholic beverages. From mimosas to bloody marys, margaritas & local craft beers, we\'ve got cocktails & brews covered.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Denver Biscuit Company',website:'denbisco.com',address:'3237 E Colfax Ave',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80206',phone:'(303) 377-7900',categories: ['Sandwiches',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Tue":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Wed":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Thu":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Fri":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Sat":"8:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Sun":"8:00 AM - 3:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Linger',website:'ediblebeats.com',address:'2030 W 30th Ave',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80211',phone:'(303) 993-3120',categories: ['Asian Fusion',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"5:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 2:30 PM,5:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 2:30 PM,5:00 PM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Housed in a former mortuary, the decor layers macabre remnants with posh details in a window-flanked space overlooking the charming Lower Highland neighborhood. The drink menu features sips and seasonings as savory as the dishes with which they\'re paired. While the rooftop patio--outfitted with 1975 GMC RV as bar and repurposed food truck as kitchen-- beckons patrons towards adventure.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Root Down',website:'rootdowndenver.com',address:'1600 W 33rd Ave',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80211',phone:'(303) 993-4200',categories: ['American (New)',' Vegan',' Vegetarian'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"4:30 PM - 9:30 PM","Tue":"4:30 PM - 9:30 PM","Wed":"4:30 PM - 9:30 PM","Thu":"4:30 PM - 9:30 PM","Fri":"4:30 PM - 10:30 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 2:30 PM,5:00 PM - 10:30 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 2:30 PM,5:00 PM - 9:30 PM"\}',about:'Root Down aims to connect the neighborhood to a dining experience in the same way ingredients are connected to food. There should be a seamless bond between the elements and experience, which stimulates the senses and draws people in.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Steuben\'s Uptown',website:'steubens.com',address:'523 E 17th Ave',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80203',phone:'(303) 830-1001',categories: ['Diners',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"9:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"9:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'A retro diner providing Regional American classics and classic cocktails.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Cherry Cricket',website:'cherrycricket.com',address:'2641 E 2nd Ave',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80206',phone:'(303) 322-7666',categories: ['Burgers',' Sports Bars',' American (New)'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Denver\'s Favorite Burger Joint since 1945. Build-Your-Own Burgers, Boozy Milkshakes, Famous Colorado Green Chili, Frings, and a Craft Beer List to Swoon Over.',history:'Established in 1945. No one really knows where the name Cherry Cricket came from, and we like it that way. We do know that Mary Zimmerman opened the original Cherry Cricket in 1945. She ran the bar out of her house, which became a watering hole and lunch counter for truck drivers and neighborhood workers. Today, we cook up award-winning burgers served with cold Colorado craft beer and a "welcome home, now sit down and enjoy" attitude.',user: User.find(9)},
