  {name:'Snooze, an A.M. Eatery',website:'snoozeeatery.com',address:'1701 Wynkoop St Ste 150',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80202',phone:'(720) 912-3152',categories: ['Breakfast & Brunch',' American (Traditional)',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Tue":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Wed":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Thu":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Fri":"6:30 AM - 2:30 PM","Sat":"6:30 AM - 4:00 PM","Sun":"6:30 AM - 4:00 PM"\}',about:'Most breakfast & brunch restaurants start with the same script: eggs, batter, coffee & a big ol\' griddle. We\'ve found scripts are a lot like pancakes, they\'re best when flipped, so we\'re always looking to turn the best breakfast classics upside-down & on their side. Stop by for delicious pancakes, french toast, benedicts, breakfast burritos, oatmeal, breakfast sandwiches, bacon & more. From paleo to vegetarian & vegan or dairy free & gluten free friendly, we\'ll happily accommodate food allergies & diets. We want each morning to feel like your weekend & happy hour rolled into one, so our restaurants feature a full bar with alcoholic beverages. From mimosas to bloody marys, margaritas & local craft beers, we\'ve got cocktails & brews covered.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Pho 95',website:'pho95noodlehouse.com',address:'1401 S Federal Blvd',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80219',phone:'(303) 936-3322',categories: ['Vietnamese',' Vegetarian',' Soup'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"9:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"9:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"9:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"9:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"9:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"9:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"9:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Fillet mignon pho, Vegetarian pho, Rice dishes, noodles bowls.',history:'Established in 2008. Pho 95 Noodle House, located in Colorado, specializes in Traditional Vietnamese food. Our award winning food and Pho soup are sure to satisfy all of the Pho-natics and first-timers alike. Pho 95 is dedicated to serving the best Vietnamese food in the Denver-Metro area! Don\'t take our word for it... Stop by one of our two different locations, Denver or Littleton and decide for yourself. We concentrate on serving genuine Vietnamese pho soup. This authentic dish usually consists of beef broth, thin slices of beef and rice noodles. Our pho soup comes in several variations; some contain soft tendon, flank, steak and brisket. People commonly like to add a hearty helping of fresh basil, beansprouts, jalapenos, lime juice, and sauces like Siracha or Hoisin sauce to their broth. For those of you that eat vegetarian, don\'t worry, we offer a vegetarian broth that caters to your needs. In addition to having a vegetarian menu, our pho soup is gluten free.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Wynkoop Brewing',website:'wynkoop.com',address:'1634 18th St',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80202',phone:'(303) 297-2700',categories: ['American (Traditional)',' Brewpubs',' Tacos'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Colorado\'s First Brewpub carrying out Denver\'s tradition of handcrafted beers and bringing people together. We promise you the best pairings of craft beer brewed fresh in house daily and food this side of the Rocky Mountains.',history:'Established in 1988. Back in 1988, when the area of LoDo was not even a thought, current Gov. Hickenlooper and three friends opened up this brewpub. The area known now as LoDo grew significantly around it. Hickenlooper took to politics and the brewpub kept doing what it does best, great food, great beer in a large atmosphere holding onto the character of its 100+ year old building.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Biker Jim\'s Gourmet Dogs',website:'bikerjimsdogs.com',address:'2148 Larimer St',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80205',phone:'(720) 746-9355',categories: ['Hot Dogs'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'We specialize in gourmet sausages. Yup, hot dogs. You will find more than 20 different dogs at any one time...and two burgers. We are a casual restaurant with a "street food" intimacy.',history:'Established in 2005. Starting with one hot dog cart on a busy street corner, we\'ve found our brick and mortar home. But, we haven\'t forgotten our roots and will keep the carts and continue to feed people, both on and off the street!',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Stout Street Social',website:'stoutstsocial.com',address:'1400 Stout St',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80202',phone:'(720) 783-3012',categories: ['American (New)',' Seafood',' Beer',' Wine & Spirits'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Marco\'s Coal Fired-Ballpark',website:'marcoscfp.com',address:'2129 Larimer St',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80205',phone:'(303) 296-7000',categories: ['Pizza',' Italian',' Beer Bar'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Marco\'s Coal-Fired specializes in true Neapolitan pizza, just the way they make it in Naples, Italy - pizza that has a crisp and chewy crust with a softer middle. From the ingredients, to the cooking techniques, and even the ovens, we are the closest thing you\'ll get to Italy in Colorado!',history:'Established in 2008. Mark Dym and Kristy Latorraca Dym opened their first pizzeria to celebrate the tradition of fine Neapolitan pizza. Instead of conforming to the American styles of pizza, Mark went directly to the source to master the art of true pizza-making from Naples, the birthplace of pizza. Voted Denver\'s best pizzeria by Westword and 5280 magazine, Marco\'s Coal-Fired started with the simple idea that passion makes great pizza. By training under the best Pizzaiuoli master craftsmen in the world, Mark and his team were awarded certification by the Associazione Verace Pizza Napoletana, and are to this day the only certified Neapolitan pizzeria in the state of Colorado. With authentic Italian pizza, we warmly welcome you to share in the experience of Pizza Fired by Passion.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Avanti Food & Beverage',website:'avantifandb.com',address:'3200 Pecos St',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80211',phone:'(720) 269-4778',categories: ['Bars',' Food Court'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:00 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:00 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'ChoLon Modern Asian - Downtown',website:'cholon.com/downtown',address:'1555 Blake St Ste 101',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80202',phone:'(303) 353-5223',categories: ['Asian Fusion',' Noodles',' Soup'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:30 AM - 8:00 PM"\}',about:'ChoLon Market, the largest Chinese-influenced market in Saigon, helped serve as inspiration for Chef Lon Symensma\'s ChoLon Bistro. The LoDo restaurant showcases his passion for Asian ingredients and French cooking techniques in a striking, eco-friendly space. ChoLon will serve lunch and dinner, as well as a small bites menu that will be available throughout the day, in a welcoming environment for all ages. The menu features inspired interpretations of traditional Asian dishes. "Many of my dishes are twists on classical Asian cuisine," says Symensma. "I look forward to sharing my own personal perspective on the flavors of Asia." The menu offers several categories designed to allow guests to sample and share many different tastes and flavors during their meal. The bar and lounge will serve handcrafted, artisanal cocktails developed to enhance Symensma\'s creations. The venue is also ideal for business meetings and presentations, featuring a large projection screen in the lounge area.',history:'Established in 2010. Iowa native Lon Symensma was 14 when he was hired at a diner and discovered how much he enjoyed the energy of a professional kitchen. In 1997 the American Culinary Federation named him National Junior Chef of the Year, after which he enrolled in the Culinary Institute of America. Following graduation he worked at a pair of Michelin two-star restaurants in the south of France and other locations in Europe. By 2001 Symensma joined esteemed chef Jean-Georges Vongerichten at his New York City restaurant, where he developed a passion for dynamic Asian ingredients. He traveled extensively in Southeast Asia and China, helping open Jean-Georges Shanghai, returning to New York City as Sous Chef for the opening of Spice Market, Jean-Georges\' Southeast Asian restaurant. Before long he was tapped to lead the kitchen of Buddakan, Stephen Starr\'s renowned New York City restaurant. After four years at Buddakan, Symensma moved to Denver in 2010 to open ChoLon Bistro, featuring modern Asian cuisine.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Tupelo Honey Southern Kitchen & Bar',website:'tupelohoneycafe.com',address:'1650 Wewatta St',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80202',phone:'(720) 274-0650',categories: ['Southern',' American (New)',' Breakfast & Brunch'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"9:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"9:00 AM - 8:00 PM"\}',about:'Tupelo Honey is a revival of Southern food and traditions rooted in the Carolina Mountains we call home. We craft brunches, lunches and suppers that bring family and friends around the table and allow for conversations and cocktails to linger longer than usual.',user: User.find(9)},
