  {name:'Toast',website:'toastfinefoodandcoffee.com',address:'2630 W Belleview Ave Ste 100',city:'Littleton',state:'CO',zipcode:'80123',phone:'(303) 797-9543',categories: ['Breakfast & Brunch',' Sandwiches',' Coffee & Tea'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Tue":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Wed":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Thu":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Fri":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Sat":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Sun":"7:00 AM - 2:00 PM"\}',about:'We are an independent restaurant specializing in upscale local-American cuisine. We start by sourcing the best local products, like rustic hand shaped bread from Izzio\'s Artisan Bakery, Polidori Sausage, fresh roasted Coda coffee and locally farmed eggs. We prepare nearly everything from scratch, from cutting our own steaks and roasting our turkeys, to grinding our own corned beef hash. After all that, we get to have a little fun with it and serve some unique items, like our savory and spicy Sante Fe French toast stuffed with eggs, chorizo, green chilies, and melted cheese, or our Nutty pancakes topped with Nutella, banana creme, and Nutter Butters. Hungry? Come visit us for what my mom says is the best breakfast and lunch in Colorado.',history:'Established in 2006. We wanted to bring outstanding breakfast and lunch dishes together with really good coffee. After leaving our restaurant and coffee shop jobs in 2005 we managed to get Toast open by December of 2006. We are located at the entrance to beautiful and historic Main Street in Littleton, on the south east corner of Santa Fe and Bowles Avenues. After winning Westwords best breakfast award from Jason Sheehan right after we opened, we found that one dining room was not enough, and then expanded into the dance studio next door. Through the years since, we have focused on making everything better with the help of our great staff.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Odyssey Italian Restaurant',website:'odysseyitalian.com',address:'603 E 6th Ave',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80203',phone:'(303) 318-0102',categories: ['Sicilian',' Seafood',' Pasta Shops'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Odyssey Sicilian Italian restaurant offers authentic dishes from the old country.fresh seafood and Colorado lamb is our specialty, Bananas foster flambe table side it is a must. Old victorian house with a romantic setting. Owners, father Ignazio and son Michele with over 50 years of experience .they are there to greet you and to accomodate your taste By visiting Odyssey it is a memorable experience Monday dinner we offer $ 8.95 pasta tasting complete dinner Buon appetito. arrivederci a presto. Drive in with Uber and we will give you $10.00 credit on your dinner check.',history:'Established in 2012. Repeat guests superb service and great food',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Bacon Social House - Sunny Side',website:'baconsocialhouse.com',address:'2434 W 44th Ave',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80211',phone:'(720) 669-7702',categories: ['American (New)',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"8:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Tue":"Closed","Wed":"8:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Thu":"8:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Fri":"8:00 AM - 3:00 PM","Sat":"8:00 AM - 3:30 PM","Sun":"8:00 AM - 3:30 PM"\}',about:'Bacon Flights, Bacon Cocktails, Diverse Menu, Brunch Cocktails, Hyper Local Craft Beer, Pancakes & Bennys.',history:'Established in 2015. Bacon Social House opened its doors on November 24, 2015 as a destination eatery with a neighborhood feel. Owner David Dill, a resident of Sunnyside, has more than 25 years of experience in running businesses as an entrepreneur and a family history of restaurant ownership. Bacon Social House is situated in Cobbler\'s Corner, an area of Sunnyside with a rich history.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Pappadeaux Seafood Kitchen',website:'pappadeaux.com',address:'7520 E Progress Pl',city:'Greenwood Village',state:'CO',zipcode:'80111',phone:'(303) 740-9449',categories: ['Seafood',' Cajun/Creole'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Convivial chain dishing up hearty portions of New Orleans-style seafood, steaks, salads & more.',history:'Established in 1976. H.D. Pappas left Greece in 1897 and traveled to America to pursue his dreams. He brought with him a passion for quality and service that became the benchmark of his success as he opened restaurants throughout Tennessee, Arkansas and Texas. It was this same dedication to quality & service that H.D. passed down to his sons and grandsons. His sons, Pete and Jim, chose a different path than their father and entered the restaurant equipment and supply business. They opened Pappas Refrigeration in 1945. Jim never dreamed that his sons would come full-circle by opening their first restaurant in 1976.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Blue Sushi Sake Grill',website:'bluesushisakegrill.com',address:'1616 16th St',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80202',phone:'(303) 640-3655',categories: ['Sushi Bars',' Japanese',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"12:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"12:00 PM - 9:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Yard House',website:'yardhouse.com',address:'1555 Court Pl',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80202',phone:'(303) 572-9273',categories: ['American (New)',' Vegetarian',' Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:00 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Yard House, the modern American gathering place where beer and food lovers unite, is an upscale, casual eatery known for great food, classic rock music, an energetic vibe and endless fleet of tap handles featuring the best American craft and import beers. Each Yard House location offers 100+ draft brews along with an array of craft cocktails. Beer is our passion, which means we\'re always staying on top of the latest and greatest brews from around the corner and around the world. At any given moment, we have 3,000 gallons of beer flowing through our keg room to 100+ taps at our center-island bar. We also have a rotating Chalkboard Series featuring unique and complex beers from local, domestic and import brewers. Our globally inspired menu features more than 100 made-from-scratch favorites, from signature starters like Poke Nachos and Fried Mac + Cheese, to street tacos, grilled burgers, pizza, seafood and steak. Each Yard House has a distinct vibe with original artwork, a hand-picked playlist of 10,000 classic songs, and glass-enclosed keg room housing up to 3,000 gallons of fresh, quality beer. Founded in Long Beach, Calif., in 1996, Yard House now spans across the U.S. with over 75 locations and is open daily for lunch, dinner, happy hour and late-night dining.',history:'Established in 1996. When the craft beer revolution started 21 years ago, Yard House had a vision - to create the largest draft beer system in the world. We took our experience with brews and breweries and coupled it with a kitchen that creates culinary innovations to be enjoyed in an energetic atmosphere.The restaurant\'s name was derived from an early Colonial tradition of serving 36-inch tall glasses - or yards - to weary stagecoach drivers. The age-old custom was a popular tradition in the early days of Yard House as guests drank beer from the signature three-foot glass vessel. Today, guests can sip their favorites from the half yard, pint glass, 23-ounce nonic glass and beer samplers.Equal to our passion for what\'s trending in beer is our interest in what\'s cropping up on today\'s innovative menus. Executive Chef Carlito Jocson is always developing new ways to fuse globally inspired flavors with favorite American dishes, giving our menu a worldly yet familiar feel.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Sassafras American Eatery, Highlands',website:'sassafrasamericaneatery.com',address:'3927 W 32nd Ave',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80212',phone:'(303) 433-0080',categories: ['Cajun/Creole',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Comfort Food'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Tue":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Wed":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Thu":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Fri":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Sat":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM","Sun":"8:00 AM - 2:00 PM"\}',about:'Sassafras is a full-service restaurant and bakery located in the Jefferson Park neighborhood of Denver. Our menu offers moderately priced comfort food influenced by Southern American cooking traditions. We are proud to create dishes using regionally local and organic ingredients. Come see and stay a while. As we like to say here at Sassafras, Welcome Home!',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Chop Shop Casual Urban Eatery Colfax',website:'coloradochopshop.com',address:'4990 E Colfax Ave',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80220',phone:'(720) 550-7665',categories: ['American (New)',' Burgers',' Salad'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 8:00 PM"\}',about:'Chop Shop Casual Urban Eatery is one of Denver\'s premier chef driven fast casual / quick serve restaurants.',history:'Established in 2014. Chop Shop was created with the idea that we deserve better options whether on the go or hanging out. We believe that great food doesn\'t need all the complications of a full service restaurant, and it should be comfortable enough to stay, hang out and enjoy a few adult beverages. At Chop Shop our main focus is to bring the freshest ingredients, highest standards, innovative techniques, and combine them with just enough service to make you comfortable and content. Our menu is seasonally crafted and prepared by chefs with a focus on clean and healthy eating, with an expansive kids menu. We also offer a tasty selection of craft beer, wine, all natural cane sodas and daily specials.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Chubby Cattle - Denver',website:'chubbycattle.com',address:'2 Broadway',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80203',phone:'(888) 887-6557',categories: ['Asian Fusion',' Hot Pot',' Sushi Bars'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"12:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"12:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"12:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"12:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"12:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"12:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"12:00 PM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'As a reformer of the traditional Mongolian cuisine, Chubby Cattle is the first restaurant in the world to combine a refrigerated, conveyer belt-based hotpot with the finest traditional hotpot from Asia. Our all-you-can-eat hotpot features fresh ingredients like A5 Wagyu. Our fresh ingredients, high-tech service system, and quality dishes will guarantee your satisfaction.',history:'Established in 2018. Managed by Chubby Cattle, Rolls brings a dining experience like never before.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Tamayo',website:'eattamayo.com',address:'1400 Larimer St',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80202',phone:'(720) 946-1433',categories: ['Mexican'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"10:30 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"10:30 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Jerusalem Restaurant',website:'jerusalemrestaurant.com',address:'1890 E Evans Ave',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80210',phone:'(303) 777-8828',categories: ['Middle Eastern',' Caterers'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"8:00 AM - 4:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"8:00 AM - 4:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"8:00 AM - 4:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"8:00 AM - 4:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"8:00 AM - 5:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"8:00 AM - 5:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"8:00 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)"\}',about:'Jerusalem Restaurant is a family-owned business serving authentic Mediterranean and Middle Easter cuisine in Denver, Colorado for over three decades. Jerusalem Restaurant is acclaimed for their authentic Mediterranean/Middle Eastern cuisine, warm hospitality and lively ambiance. Jerusalem Restaurant provides traditional recipes that contain robust flavors of the Mediterranean region prepared with the freshest ingredients obtained locally. Jerusalem Restaurant strives to provide the Denver community with healthy, fresh, and nutritional Middle Eastern Cuisine in a relaxed and casual dining atmosphere. Our menu features many traditional staples of the Mediterranean Diet, as well as offering original dishes with recipes that have stemmed down from generation to generation at the best value in town.',history:'Established in 1978. Jerusalems was opened in 1978 by a hard working family. This mom&pop restaurant soon grew to become a landmark in Denver with customers from all around the US. We thrive on your satisfaction and it is because of you all that we are still here.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Star Kitchen',website:'starkitchenco.com',address:'2917 W Mississippi Ave Ste 5',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80219',phone:'(303) 936-0089',categories: ['Dim Sum',' Seafood',' Cantonese'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"10:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"10:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"Closed","Thu":"10:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"10:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Sat":"10:30 AM - 9:00 PM","Sun":"10:30 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(9)},
