  {name:'Bistro Vendome',website:'bistrovendome.com',address:'2267 Kearney St',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80207',phone:'(303) 825-3232',categories: ['French',' Venues & Event Spaces'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"4:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"9:00 AM - 2:00 PM,4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"9:00 AM - 2:00 PM,4:00 PM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Bistro Vendôme reflects our desired image in the community: a local favorite in a downtown rich with history that offers an exceptional dining experience in a charming, neighborhood setting.',history:'Established in 2003. At the hands of owners Chef Jennifer Jasinski and Beth Gruitch, Bistro Vendôme has become the French destination of Historic Larimer Square.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Barcelona Wine Bar RiNo',website:'barcelonawinebar.com',address:'2900 Larimer St',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80205',phone:'(303) 816-3300',categories: ['Tapas/Small Plates',' Wine Bars',' Spanish'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"4:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"4:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"4:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"2:00 PM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"2:00 PM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"11:00 AM - 1:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Ace Eat Serve',website:'acedenver.com',address:'501 E 17th Ave',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80203',phone:'(303) 800-7705',categories: ['Bars',' Asian Fusion',' Ramen'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"4:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"4:00 PM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Ace Eat Serve is a restaurant, bar, and ping pong hall that combines Asian-inspired cuisine with an extensive bar program that includes craft cocktails & beer, wine, sake, and housemade soda. The recipient of the 2012 Mayor\'s Design Award, Ace Eat Serve\'s build-out utilizes many recycled and repurposed materials in its three distinct areas--the dining room, spacious outdoor patio, and indoor ping pong room, which features eight full-size pong tables. Ace Eat Serve also specializes in hosting small and large scale events including birthday and anniversary parties, corporate team-building events, holiday parties, and many others. Additional event information is available on Ace Eat Serve\'s website.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Fire On The Mountain',website:'fotmdenver.com',address:'3801 W 32nd Ave',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80211',phone:'(303) 480-9464',categories: ['Chicken Wings',' Bars',' American (Traditional)'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Fire on the Mountain - Highlands provides a family friendly dining experience in northwest Denver\'s Highlands neighborhood. We source our products with integrity and serve all natural, sustainably raised chicken and Colorado grass fed beef. We make each of our twelve wing sauces in-house every day, as well as awesome hand cut fries, fantastic salads, and other goodies. We also specialize in local craft beers and delicious specialty cocktails!',history:'Established in 2012. Our good friends Jordan Busch and Sara Sawicki founded Fire on the Mountain in Portland, Oregon, in 2005. The original FOTM is a tiny hole in the wall on North Interstate St. In 2008 Jordan and Sara expanded to another location on East Burnside and in 2011 opened a third FOTM restaurant and brewery on in NE Portland. Now in 2012 we are proud to establish the Rocky Mountain outpost of Fire on the Mountain and let Denver in on this Portland cult favorite!',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Fruition Restaurant',website:'fruitionrestaurant.com',address:'1313 E 6th Ave',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80218',phone:'(303) 831-1962',categories: ['American (New)',' Bars'],price:'$$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"5:00 PM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"5:00 PM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Chef Alex Seidel specializes in upscale American comfort food prepared seasonally with a changing menu.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Adelitas Cocina Y Cantina',website:'adelitasco.com',address:'1294 S Broadway',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80210',phone:'(303) 778-1294',categories: ['Mexican',' Breakfast & Brunch',' Cocktail Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"Closed","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 11:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'Adelitas Cocina y Cantina Denver brings traditional Mexican fare, and tequila cocktails to your Platt Park neighborhood. We bring you a relaxing, comfortable, safe and enjoyable atmosphere, along with traditional Mexican food from the state of Michocan, Mexico. We offer brunch, lunch, and dinner 7 days a week, and a late night menu to satisfy your late night cravings. We operate as a family orientated restaurant, but do not worry, after 9pm we will dim the lights, and provide you with a warm, relaxing environment.',history:'Established in 2013. "La Adelita" is the folk tale of a young woman who fell in love with a sergeant during the Mexican Revolution, left her humble home behind, and traveled with him and his regiment. "La Adelita" became an archetype of a woman warrior during this era. She was a soldadera, or woman soldier, who took on various supporting roles to her beloved. She prepared meals, mended clothing, cared for the wounded, and even fought in battles against Mexican government forces. With the passage of time, the word "Adelita" came to be used for all of the soldaderas, marking their place in history as a vital force in the Mexican revolutionary war efforts. The term "La Adelita" symbolizes a brave, altruistic woman with an abundance of strength and courage.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Happy Camper - Denver',website:'happycamper.pizza',address:'3211 N Pecos St',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80211',phone:'(720) 259-1044',categories: ['Pizza',' Bars'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"10:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Tue":"10:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Wed":"10:30 AM - 12:00 AM (Next day)","Thu":"10:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Fri":"10:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sat":"9:30 AM - 2:00 AM (Next day)","Sun":"9:30 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'PLEASE NOTE: Happy Camper is a 21+ establishment. All patrons must show legal identification to enter. Minors are permitted with their parent Monday - Friday before 7pm and must be off-premise by 9pm and Saturday - Sunday before 2pm and must be off-premise by 4pm. Reservation required.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Esters Virginia Village',website:'estersdenver.com',address:'1950 S Holly St',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80222',phone:'(303) 955-4904',categories: ['Pizza',' American (New)',' Pubs'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"10:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"10:00 AM - 10:00 PM"\}',about:'*Kitchen & bar closes at 10pm nightly, last call for bar is 9:45pm *we do NOT offer delivery at this time, thanks for the understanding!',history:'Established in 2015. Started by long standing craft beer employees, Esters is a labor of love for community, family and good times.',user: User.find(9)},
  {name:'Park Burger - Pearl',website:'parkburger.com',address:'1890 S Pearl St',city:'Denver',state:'CO',zipcode:'80210',phone:'(720) 242-9951',categories: ['Burgers',' Beer Bar'],price:'$$',hours:'\{"Mon":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Tue":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Wed":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Thu":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM","Fri":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sat":"11:00 AM - 10:00 PM","Sun":"11:00 AM - 9:00 PM"\}',about:'Park Burger is a casual, family-friendly neighborhood restaurant, serving DenverÕs prizewinning burgers, fries, shakes, and beer. At Park Burger, we pride ourselves on crafting the best burger using only the freshest, highest quality ingredients. We start with anatural, never frozen beef, buffalo, and house made turkey and veggie burger patties, all served on locally baked buns made exclusively for Park Burger.',user: User.find(9)},
